\id ACT - Gamo project
\h Hawaareta Ooso
\toc1 Hawaareta Ooso
\toc2 Hawaareta Ooso
\toc3 Hawa
\mt1 Hawaareta Ooso
\imt1 Giddo qofa
\ip Hawaareta ooso maxaafazi Luqaassa Mishiraachcho qaalappe kaallizayssa. Ha maxaafazas ayfe qofay koyro Yesusa kaallizayti Xillo Ayanay kaalethin iza gish yootiza Mishiraachcho qaala “Yerusalamen, Yuhuda dere ubban, Samaariyaninne biitta gaxa gakkanaas” 1:8 Mishiraachcho qaala isti wosti wursi gaththidakkone hessa yootanassa. Maxaafazi ammanoy Ayhudata garsan doommidi kumeththa alame asay ammanana gakkanaas izi waani waani aakki aakki bidakkonne yootizayssa. Hayssa maxaafa xaafidayssi ammanizayti Oroome kawora eqetanas garsara yo7o qachizayta gidontayssanne ammanizayta ammanoy hanko Ayhudata ammano polokko gathizaz gididayssa erissanas daro baaxetides.
\ip Hawaareta Ooso maxaafay Yesusa gish Mishiraachcho qaalay gakkizasoy woden woden aakki aakki bizayssanne Woosa Keeththey minni xaphidayssa bessiza heedzdzu gita kifiletan shaaketanas dandayees.
\ip 1. Ammanizayta ammanoy Yesusi dendidi pude salo bidappe guye Yerusalamen doommides.
\ip 2. Isra7eele dere kumeth gakkides.
\ip 3. Oroome gujji ekkidi Mediteraane abba yuushon diza deraa gakkanaas oykkoyssa yootees.
\ip Hawaareta Ooso maxaafan keehi qonci beettizay Xillo Ayana ooso gidishin Phenxaqoste ba7aale gallas Yerusalamen ammaniza asa bolla wolqara wodhdhoyssa, hessathoka he maxaafazan yootetida yootan ubban qoncida mala Xillo Ayanay Woosa Keeththanne Woosa Keeththa kaalethizayta kaalethidayssanne minthethidayssa gujees. Beni wode yootetiza ammano qaalay dumma dumma ogera sabaketides. Hawaareta ooso maxaafan poletida oosotikka kiitazi ammanizayta de7onne ista issifetethan diza wolqay ay mala minokkone eriseetes.
\is1 Ha maxaafay oykkida kumeththa qofa
\io1 Markatethas giigeteth 1:1-26
\io1 Yerusalamen yootetida markateth 2:1-8:3
\io1 Yuhudaninne Samaariyan yootetida markateth 8:4-12:25
\io1 Phawuloosa Hawaaretetha ooththo 13:1-28:31
\io1 Mishiraachcho qaala yootanas Phawuloosas koyro buus 13:1-14:28
\io1 Yerusalame shiiqo 15:1-35
\io1 Mishiraachcho qaala yootanas Phawuloosas nam7antho buus 15:36-18:22
\io1 Mishiraachcho qaala yootanas Phawuloosas heedzdzantho buus 18:23-21:16
\io1 Phawuloosi Yerusalamen, Qisaareninne Oroomen qashettides 21:17-28:31
\c 1
\s1 Hawaareta Ooso Geeshsha Maxaafa
\p 
\v 1 Tofiloosa, Yesusi ooththanassinne tamarsanas oykkidayssa wursa ta nees koyro maxaafan xaafadis. \x * \xo 1:1 \xt Luqa 1:1-4\x*
\v 2 Hessika izi pude dentha gallas gakkanaas ba doori kiittidaytas Xillo Ayana baggara izi istas immida azazokko.
\v 3 Izi daro waaye beyidappe guye Istako shiiqidi hayqoppe dendanayssa istas daro markara qoncisishe oyddu tammu gallas gakkanaas istas gallas gallas beettishe Xoossa Kawoteththa gish yootides.
\v 4 Istara issife maaddan utti dishe ista “Yerusalameppe kezoppite; gido attin ta intes yootishin inte siyidayssa ta Aaway immida ufayssa naagite. \x * \xo 1:4 \xt Luqa 24:49\x*
\v 5 Yohannisi haaththan xammaqides shin inte qas guuththa wodeppe guye Xillo Ayanan xammaqettana” giidi azazides. \x * \xo 1:5 \xt Mato 3:11; Mar 1:8; Luqa 3:16; Yoha 1:33\x*
\p 
\v 6 Istika issi bolla shiiqeti dishe “Godo! Ne Isra7eeleta kawoteth zaarada ha7i essanee?” gi oychida.
\p 
\v 7 Izikka istas “Aaway ba shenen woththida wode eroy intes imettibenna.
\v 8 Gido attin Xillo Ayanay inte bolla wodhdhida wode inte wolqa ekkana. Yerusalamenka, Yuhudanikka, Samaariyanka ubbason biitta gaxa gakkanaas inte taas markata gidana” gides. \x * \xo 1:8 \xt Mato 28:19; Mar 16:15; Luqa 24:47-48\x*
\p 
\v 9 Hessa gi yootidappe guye isti xeellishin pude salo dendides. Salo shaaraykka ista ayfeppe iza geenthides. \x * \xo 1:9 \xt Mar 16:19; Luqa 24:50-51\x*
\p 
\v 10 Izi bishin isti iza tishshi histi pude salo xeellishin booththa may7o may7ida nam7u asati qopponta ista achchan eqqidi;
\v 11 “Inteno Galila asato! Inte pude salo xeellishe hayssan aazas eqqidetii? Hayssi inte matappe pude salo dendishin inte beyiza Yesusi salo kezishin inte beyida mala hessathoka izi ha simmi yaana” gida.
\s1 Yuhuda sohon Matiyasi doorettides
\p 
\v 12 Hessafe guye Dabrazayte geetettiza zuma bollafe wodhdhidi Yerusalame simmida. He zumaykka Yerusalameppe issi kilo metre mala haakkees.
\v 13 Gede katamayo gelida wode kase ba diza keeththa Pooqe bolla kezida; heytikka Phexroosa, Yohannisa, Yaqoobe, Indiraasa, Piliphoosa, Toomaasa, Bartelemoosa, Matoosa, Ilfiyoosa naa Yaqoobe, ba bagga maaddizade geetettiza Simoonanne Yaqoobe naa Yuhuda. \x * \xo 1:13 \xt Mato 10:2-4; Mar 3:16-19; Luqa 6:14-16\x*
\v 14 Heyti wurikka macasatappe Yesusa aayo Maaramira hessathoka iza ishatara issi woznan issi bolla qanxonta minni woossida.
\p 
\v 15 He gallasatan Phexroosi xeetanne nam7u tammu ammaniza asa giddon eqqidi,
\v 16 “Ta ishato! Yesusa oykkida asata kaalethi ehida. Yuhuda gish Xillo Ayanay kasetidi Dawute duunan haasayida Geeshsha maxaafa qaalay polettana koshshees.
\v 17 Izikka nuuppe issade mala taybettidi hayssa ha oosozan gellanas qaada demmides” gides.
\p 
\v 18 Gidikkoka hayssadey ba iita ooson demmida miishan gade shamides; henka ba liiphen gufanni kundin iza asatethay giddofe phalqeti wodhdhides; iza maracey biitta bolla zaazetides. \x * \xo 1:18 \xt Mato 27:3-8\x*
\v 19 Hessika Yerusalamen diza asas ubbas siyettides. Biittaykka ista qaalara “Akeldama” geetettides; hessas birsheththayka suutha biitta guussa.
\p 
\v 20 Gujjidikka Phexroosi “Mazamure maxaafan
\q2 ‘Iza gadey mela atto, izan ay asikka dooppo;
\q3 qasseka iza daannateth hara asi ekko’
\q2 geetetti xaafettides. \x * \xo 1:20 \xt Maza 69:25; 109:8\x*
\p 
\v 21 “Hessa gish Goda Yesusi nunara diza wode ubban nunara issife dizayta giddofe nu issade dooranas koshshees.
\v 22 Hessika Yohannisa xinqateppe haa simmin Yesusi nuuppe shaaketi dendi baana gakkanaas nunara dizadde gidanas bessees. Gaasoyka ha asatappe issadey nunara Yesusa denthas marka gidana koshshees” gides. \x * \xo 1:22 \xt Mato 3:16; Mar 1:9; 16:19; Luqa 3:21; 24:51\x*
\p 
\v 23 Hessa gish Barsabaasa woykko Yosxoosa geetettiza Yoosefenne Maatiyaasa nam7ata shiishshidi,
\v 24 “Godo! Ne asa ubba wozna eraasa; hayta nam7ata giddofe ne oona dooridakko issade nuna bessa.
\v 25 Yuhuday yeggi bidason ha oosa ooththanadenne Hawaare gidanadde ne doora” gi woossida.
\v 26 Hessafe saama yeggin saamay Maatiyaasas kezides. Izikka tammanne issi Hawaaretara issife tayibettides.
\c 2
\s1 Xillo Ayanay ammaniza asa bolla wodhdhides
\p 
\v 1 Phenxaqoste geetettiza ba7aale gallassi gakkida wode asay wurikka issi soon shiiqi dishin;
\v 2 qofay baynda daro mino gote carko mala giirissi yides; asay diza keeththakka kumides.
\v 3 Tama laco inxarsa malay asas beettidi shaaketi shaaketi issi issi asa bolla uttides.
\v 4 Ammanizayti wuri Xillo Ayanan kumidi Ayanay istas haasayanas immidayssa keena hara qaalara haasaya oykkida.
\p 
\v 5 He wode salo gufanthon diza dereppe yida Xoossas babbiza Ayhudati Yerusalamen deettes.
\v 6 He giirissa siydi derey shiiqides. Issi issi asay ba qaalara haasayizayssa siydi malalettida.
\v 7 Malaletidinne gaanazi dhayin “Hayti haasayizayti wurikka Galila as deettenee?
\v 8 Histin nuni nu yeletida nu dere qaalara isti haasayishin wosti siyizonii?
\v 9 Nuni Pharteena asay, Meede asay, Eelaame asay, Mesopotoomiyan, Yuhudan, Qophodooqiyan, Phanxoosan, Iisiyan,
\v 10 Firgiyan, Phinfiliyan, Gibxen, Qareena achchan diza Liibiyappenne Oroomeppe yidayti
\v 11 Ayhudatinne gede Ayhudatethan gelida Qarxeese asanne Araabe asata gidishin Xoossa wolqama oosoza hayti nu qaalara haasayishin nu siyoos” gida.
\p 
\v 12 Wurikka keehi malalettidinne gaanazi dhayin ba giddon “Hayssi aazeshaa?” geetettida.
\v 13 Bagga asay “Hayti daro woyne cajje uyida” giidi ista qidhida.
\p 
\v 14 He wode Phexroosi tammanne issinetara eqqidinne ba qaala dhoqu histidi deraas hizgides “Inteno Yuhuda asato! Yerusalamen dizayto! Inte wurikka hayssa issi miish eritenne ta gizayssa siyite.
\v 15 Ha7i gadey wontin buro heedzdzu saate gidida gish inte qoppiza mala hayti asati mathotibeetenna.
\v 16 Gido attin hayssi kase nabe Iyu7eelen hizgi yootetida qaalay poletanassa,
\q1 
\v 17 ‘Xoossi Wursetha gallas
\q3 ta Ayana asho may7ida ubba bolla ta gussana;
\q2 inte maca naytinne inte attuma nayti tinbite haasayana;
\q3 yelaga nayti ajjuta beyana;
\q3 Cimati agumo agumettana. \x * \xo 2:17 \xt Iyu 2:28-32\x*
\q1 
\v 18 He wode ta maca ashkarata bollanne ta attuma ashkarata bolla
\q3 ta Ayanappe ta gussana.
\q3 Istika tinbite haasayana.
\q1 
\v 19 Bolla Salon malalisiza hanota ta bessana,
\q3 garsa sa7an malatata ta bessana;
\q3 suuthi, tamaynne tulalay hanana.
\q1 
\v 20 Gitanne boncho gidida
\q3 Goda gallassi yaanappe kasetidi
\q3 awa arshey dhumana;
\q3 Aginaykka suuth misatana.
\q1 
\v 21 Goda sunth xeygizay wuri attana’ gides.
\p 
\v 22 “Isra7eele nayto! Hayssa qaala siyite; inte inte baggara erizayssa mala inte giddon malatanne asi siyi eronta miishata iza kushen ooththidi Xoossi Naazirete Yesusas markatides.
\v 23 Xoossi kase ba qachidayssa izas beni eratetha mala hayssade inte kushen aaththi immides. Inteka iita asata kushen kaqeti hayqqana mala ooththideta. \x * \xo 2:23 \xt Mato 27:35; Mar 15:24; Luqa 23:33; Yoha 19:18\x*
\v 24 Gido attin Xoossi iza bollafe hayqo wolqa diggidi hayqoppe denthides. Hayqoyka iza oykki ashshanas dandaybenna. \x * \xo 2:24 \xt Mato 28:5-6; Mar 16:6; Luqa 24:5\x*
\v 25 Dawuteykka iza gish
\q2 ‘Tani Goda ubba wode ta sinthan beyays;
\q3 izi ta ushachan dees; mulekka hirgike.
\q1 
\v 26 Hessa gish ta woznay ufayetees;
\q3 ta duunaykka galatees;
\q3 ta ashoy ufayssan daana.
\q1 
\v 27 Ne ta shempoyo Duufon aggaka;
\q3 ne naa geeshshaza wooqana mala aggaggakka.
\q1 
\v 28 Ne de7o oge ta erana mala ooththadasa.
\q3 Ne tanara diza gish ta ufayssay kumeththa’
\p 
\v 29 “Ta ishato! Beni aawatappe Dawutey hayqqi moogetiddayssanne iza duufoy hach gakkanaas nu achchan dizayssa babbonta ta intes yootana danda7ays.
\v 30 Izi nabe gidida gish Xoossi iza zerethafe issade iza kawoteththa alga bolla wothanayssa kase caaqo qaalan yootidayssa erides. \x * \xo 2:30 \xt Maza 132:11; 2Same 7:12-13\x*
\v 31 Hessa kasetidi erida gishshinne iza ashoy wooqi Duufon attonta doorettida Kirstoosa dentha gish haasayides.
\v 32 He Yesusa Xoossi hayqoppe denthides. Nukka wuri hayssas markata.
\v 33 Hessa gish izi Xoossa ushachchan dhoqu dhoqu gidappe guye Xillo Ayana ufaysa ba aawappe ekkidi ha7i inte beyizayssanne siyizayssa duge gussides.
\v 34-35 Dawutey pude salo kezibenna; izi ba duunan
\q2 ‘Goday ta Godas “Ta ne morketa
\q3 ne toho garsan yedhissana gakkanaas
\q3 ta ushachchan utta” gides.’ \x * \xo 2:34-35 \xt Maza 110:1\x*
\p 
\v 36 “Hessa gish Xoossi inte kaqqida Yesusa Godanne Kirstoosa histidayssa Isra7eele asay wuri lo7ethi ero” gides.
\p 
\v 37 Derey hessa siyida mala woznay boshettides. Phexroosanne hanko Yesusi kiittidayta “Nu ishato! Histin nu ay ooththinoo?” gida.
\p 
\v 38 Phexroosikka “Maarotethan gelite; inte nagaray maarettana mala intefe issi issi asi Yesus Kirstoosa sunthan xammaqettite; izi immiza Xillo Ayana inte ekkana.
\v 39 Ufayssa qaalay intessinne inte naytassa; qasseka Goda Xoossi baako xeygiza haahon dizaytassara ubbassa” gides.
\p 
\v 40 Hara daro qaalara istas markatishe “Hayssa geella yeletethafe intena ashshite” giidi ista qofisides.
\v 41 He gallas qaala ekkidaytinne xammaqetidayti heedzdzu shi mala asay kaseyta bolla gujettides.
\v 42 Istika Hawaareta timirten, issife quma muussaninne woossan minnida.
\p 
\v 43 Hawaareta kushen daro malatati oosettida gish asi ubbay istas babbides.
\v 44 Ammanidayti wurikka issife de7ida; baas dizazikka ubba issi bolla go7ettida. \x * \xo 2:44 \xt Hawa 4:32-35\x*
\v 45 Baas diza miishenne mehe bayzi bayzi ba giddon koshshida mala gishechchida.
\v 46 Gallas gallas Xoossa Keeththan issife shiiqetes. Ba keeththanka quma issife ufayssaninne suure woznara meetes.
\v 47 Isti Xoossa galatishe dere sinthan bonchettida. Godayka ista bolla gallas gallas oorath ammanizayta gujjides.
\c 3
\s1 Phexroosi issi tohoy silidade pathides
\p 
\v 1 Issi wode gallassafe uddufun saate bolla Phexroosinne Yohannisi woossa saaten Xoossa Keeththe baana kezida.
\v 2 Issi yeletosappe doommidi tohoy silidade Xoossa Keeththe geliza asappe miishe woossana mala asay gallas gallas tookki efidi woththin issi “Lo7o” geetettiza Xoossa Keeththa pengen woossizadey dees.
\p 
\v 3 Izikka Phexroosinne Yohannisi Xoossa Keeththe gelishin beyida istafe miishe woossides.
\v 4 Phexroosinne Yohannisi iza tishshi histi xeellida. Phexroosikka iza “Ane haa nuna xeella” gides.
\v 5 Addezikka istafe aykko demmana giidi ista tishshi histi xeellides.
\v 6 Gido attin Phexroosi izas zaaridi “Taas biraynne worqay deenna; gidikkokka taas dizaz ta nees immays; Naazirete Yesus Kirstoosa sunthan dendada ne tohora hamuta” gides.
\v 7 Izas ushachcha kushe oykkidi denthides. Heerakka addeza tohoynne toho qirphey minnides.
\v 8 Guppi dendi eqqidi hamuth oykkides. Yaanne haanne hamutishenne guppishe Xoossaka galatishe istara issife Xoossa Keeththa gibbe gelides.
\v 9 Izi Xoossa galatishe yaanne haane simerettishin asay beyides.
\v 10 Hayssadey hannife kase “Lo7o” geetettiza Xoossa Keeththa pengen uttidi miishe woossizay iza gididayssa erides. Iza bolla hanidayssafe dendidayssan asay keehi malaletides.
\s1 Phexroosa haasaya
\p 
\v 11 Ha paxida woossanchay Phexroosakonne Yohannisakko shiph giidi istara oykketi dishin derey wuri malaletidi istako “Solomoone simeretethaso” geetettizaso wothan yides.
\v 12 Phexroosi he asa beyidi “Inteno Isra7eele dereto! Hayssan aazas malaletetii? Qasseka hayssa addeza nuni nu wolqan woykko nuni nu xillotethan pathidi hamutissida mala qoodidi nuna aazas tishshi histi xeelletii?
\v 13 Nu aawanta Abrahaamenta, Yisaaqanta, Yaqoobenta Xoossi ba naaza Yesusa bonchides. Inte qas iza hayqos aaththi immideta; Philaxoosi izi birshana koynka inte ‘Koyokko’ gideta. \x * \xo 3:13 \xt Kessa 3:15\x*
\v 14 Geeshshanne xilloza inte kadidi shempo wodhizayssi birshettana mala woossideta. \x * \xo 3:14 \xt Mato 27:15-23; Mar 15:6-14; Luqa 23:13-23; Yoha 19:12-15\x*
\v 15 De7o immizade inte wodhideta; gido attin Xoossi iza hayqoppe denthides; hessas nuni marka.
\v 16 Hayssi inte beyizayssinne inte erizayssi minni eqqiday Yesusa sunthan ammanida gishassa. Inte wurikka beyiza mala izi kumeththa paxa demmiday Yesusa sunthaninne iza sunthan beettiza ammanona.
\p 
\v 17 “Ha7ikka ta ishato! Inte hessa ooththiday inte halaqata mala eronta gididayssa ta erays.
\v 18 Gidikkoka Kirstoosi waaye ekkanayssa Xoossi kase nabeta duunan haasayidayssa polides.
\v 19 Hessa gish inte nagaray qucceti dhayana mala maarotethan gelite. Inte biza ogeppe simmite; Goda matappe inte ooraxana wodey intes yaana.
\v 20 Qasseka Xoossi kase intes doori woththida Yesus Kirstoosa izi intes yeddana.
\v 21 Xoossi kase geeshsha nabeta duunan haasayidayssa mala hanizayssa wursi ooraxissana wodey gakkanaas izi salon gam7anas koshshees.
\v 22 Museykka ‘Inte Goda Xoossay inte giddofe ta mala nabe intes denthana. Izi intes yootizayssa siyite. \x * \xo 3:22 \xt Zaare 18:15,18\x*
\v 23 He nabeza siyonta ixida shempoy wuri dere giddofe shaaketi dhayo’
\p 
\v 24 “Tumappe Sameelappe ha simmin dendida nabeti wuri hayta wodeta gish haasayida.
\v 25 Inteka nabeta nayta. Qasseka Xoossi Abrahaames ‘Ne zerethan biitta asi wuri anjettana’ giidi izi caaqida caaqoza inte laattana. \x * \xo 3:25 \xt Medhe 22:18\x*
\v 26 Xoossi naaza denthida wode intena issa issa inte iitatethafe zaaridi anjana mala kasetidi inteko kiittides” gides.
\c 4
\s1 Phexroosinne Yohannisi Ayhuda duulataso shiiqida
\p 
\v 1 Phexroosinne Yohannisi asas haasayan dishin Qeeseta Halaqatinne Xoossa Keeththa naagizayta halaqay qasseka Saduqaaweti akekonta istako yida. \f + \fr 4:1 \fq Qeeseta \ft Issi issi Geeshsha Maxaafati Qeeseta halaqa geettes.\f*
\v 2 Yiidinne Hawaareti asa tamarsizayssassinne Yesusa baggara bettida hayqqidayta dentha gish sabakizayssas keehi hanqettida.
\v 3 Phexroosanne Yohannisa gadey qammishin oykidi wontana gakkanaas qasho keeththan ayssida.
\v 4 Gido attin qaala siyida asappe dariza baggay ammanides. Ammaniza attuma asata qooday gede ichashu shi gakkanaas dhoqu gides.
\p 
\v 5 Wontetha gallas ista halaqatinne cimati qasseka Muse woga tamarsizayti Yerusalamen shiiqida.
\v 6 Ista Qeeseta halaqa Haanaynne Qayaafay, Yohannisi, Iskindirosinne Qeeseta halaqaso asay wuri he gadaan bettida.
\v 7 Istika Phexroosanne Yohannisa ba giddon aaththi essidi “Hayssa inte ooththizay aaza wolqanee? Woykko oona sunthanee?” giidi oychida.
\p 
\v 8 He wode Phexroosi Xillo Ayanan kumidi “Inteno dere halaqato! Dere cimato!
\v 9 Inte hach ha toho sila addezas oosettida lo7o oosoy waani izi paxidakko inte nuna oychiza gidikko,
\v 10 inte kaqqin Xoossi hayqoppe denthida Naazirete Yesus Kirstoosa sunthan izi paxidayssanne inte sinthan izi eqidayssa inteka Isra7eele dere asay wuri hayssa erite.
\v 11 Izikka inte keeththa hiillati leqqi aggida shuchchay ginbe keeththas gula bolla bollara woththiza shuch gidides.\f + \fr 4:11 \fq gula gizayssa issi issi bagga gaammo asay magala woyko shocha shuch gees.\f*\x * \xo 4:11 \xt Maza 118:22\x*
\v 12 Atotethi hara oonanka ba; saloppe garsa baggara nu asa nayti attana mala nuus imettiday hayssafe hara sunthi deenna” gides.
\p 
\v 13 Ayhudata duulata asaykka Phexroosinne Yohannisi hessatho xali haasayizayssa beyidi isti tamaronta as gididayssa eridi malaletidanne isti kase Yesusara dizayta gididayssa akeekida.
\v 14 He paxida addezi istara eqqidishin beyida gish istas hara ooththanas gaasoy dhayides.
\v 15 Hessa gish ista duulatappe kessana mala azazida. Hessafe qasseka shiiqetidi ba giddon zoretida.
\v 16 Ba giddon “Hayta asata wostinoo? Yerusalamen diza asay wuri ista kushen hanida gita malata erides. Hessa gish nu ha yo7oza asa baleththanas dandayokko.
\v 17 Gido attin hayssi yo7ozi dere giddon keehi aakkonta malanne hayti asati nam7antho hayssa ha sunthan hara oonaska yootonta mala istas lo7ethi yootana” gida.
\p 
\v 18 Ista xeygidinne mulekka Yesusa sunthan haasayonta malanne tamarsonta mala azazida.
\v 19 Phexroosinne Yohannisi qasse zaaridi “Nuni Xoossafe bollara intes azazettanas bessizakonne ane inte Xoossa sinthan pirdite.
\v 20 Nuni nu beyidayssanne nu siyidayssa haasayanappe guye gookko” gida.
\p 
\v 21 Qasseka ista bolla mandidi yeddida. Gaasoyka hanko derey wuri hanida yo7oza gaason wurikka Xoosse galatiza gish ista qaxayanas dandaybetenna.
\v 22 He gita malatan paxida addezas laythi oyddu tammafe bolla.
\p 
\v 23 Phexroosinne Yohannisi qashoppe birshettidi gede ba asatakko simmidi Qeeseta Halaqatinne Dere cimati ista gidayssa wursika yootida.
\v 24 Istika hessa siyida mala ba qaala dhoqu histidi issife Xoossakko “Wogga Godawu! Neni salonne sa7a, abbanne abba giddon dizayta wursa medhadassa. \x * \xo 4:24 \xt Kessa 20:11; Nahi 9:6; Maza 146:6\x*
\v 25 Ne ashkara nuus aawa Dawute duunara Xillo Ayanan
\q2 ‘Dere asay aazas hanqetti dendidee?
\q3 Derey aazas mela maqetizee?
\q1 
\v 26 Biitta kawoti issife gaaggidi
\q3 biitta haarizayti issi bolla shiiqettidi
\q2 Goda bollan ne dooretti tiyettidayssa bolla duulatida’
\m giidi waassida.
\p 
\v 27 “Tumappe Herdoossinne Phanxoosa Philaxoosi Isra7eelataranne hara dere asara hanno katamayn ne doora tiyida geeshsha naaza Yesusa bolla yo7o qachanas shiiqetida. \x * \xo 4:27 \xt Luqa 23:1,7-11; Mato 27:1-2; Mar 15:1; Yoha 18:28-29\x*
\v 28 Hayssanka ne wolqaninne ne shenen kase ne qoppidayssa isti polida.
\v 29 Godo! Ha7ikka ista mandeza ne beya; nuni ne aylleti ne qaala babbonta kumeththa xalatethara yootana mala dandayissa.
\v 30 Pathanas ne kushe micca. Ne naa geeshshaza sunthan gita malata ooththa” gida.
\p 
\v 31 Isti woossidappe guye isti dizasoy qaaxides. Wurikka Xillo Ayanan kumidi Xoossa qaala xalatethan yootida.
\s1 Ammanizayta issifetetha duus
\p 
\v 32 Ammanizayti wurikka issi woznaninne issi qofan gaaggi deettes. Istas dizay wuri issi bolla dees attin baas dizaz “Hayssi taas buzo miisha” gizaddey deenna. \x * \xo 4:32 \xt Hawa 2:44-45\x*
\v 33 Hawaaretikka Goda Yesusa dentha gita wolqan markateth oykkida. Ubba bolla gita Xoossa kiyatethi dees.
\v 34 Ista giddon metotanchay issadeykka baawa. Gaasoyka gade gidin keeththe gidin baas diza wursi bayzi bayzi shiishida miish
\v 35 Hawaareta kushen woththidi issi issades izas koshshiza mala gisheettes.
\p 
\v 36 Qophiroose geetettizason diza Yoosefe geetettizadey issi Lewe bagga asi dees. Izikka Hawaaretan “Barnabaasa” geetetti summides. Hessas birsheththay “Minthetho naa” guussa.
\v 37 Izikka ba gade bayzida miisha ehidi Hawaareta kushen woththides.
\c 5
\s1 Hananiyanne Saphphira
\p 
\v 1 Issi Hananiya geetettiza asi Saphphira geetettiza ba macheyra ba gade bayzides.
\v 2 Macheya Saphphiray lo7etha erishin gadeza bayzida miishafe bagga shaakki ashshidi bagga ehidi Hawaareta kushen immides.
\v 3-4 Qasse Phexroosi “Haysso Hananiya! Neni Xillo Ayana bolla wordotanassinne gade miishafe ashshana mala Xala7ey ays ne woznan gelidee? Bayzanappe kase gadezi neyssa gidenee? Ne bayzidappe guye qasse miishay ne kushen deenee? Histin ne hayssa mala wosta ne woznan qoppadii? Ne Xoossa bolla wordotadassa attin asa bolla gidenna” gides.
\p 
\v 5 Hessa siyida mala Hananiyay kundi hayqqides. Hessa siyida asay wuri daro babbides.
\p 
\v 6 Attumasay dendidi aha xaaxidinne heerakka efidi moogides.
\p 
\v 7 Heedzdzu saateppe guye macheya izi waanidakkonne eronta dashe yadus.
\v 8 Phexroosikka “Ane taas yoota; inte gadeza bayzida waagay hanno xallaa?” gides. Izakka “Ee hanno ha waagayn bayzidos” gadus.
\p 
\v 9 Phexroosikka “Inte Xoossa Ayana paacanas aysi issi duuna gididetii? Hekko ne azina moogida asati moogi simmidi karen penge bolla deettes. Isti nenakka kessi ekki efana” gides.
\v 10 Iza siyida mala heerakka iza toho bolla kundada hayqqadus. Attumasaykka soo gelida mala hayqqidaro beyidi kessi efidi izi azina achchan moogida.
\v 11 Kumeththa Woosa Keeththa asaynne hessa siyida asay wuri daro babbides.
\s1 Hawaareta kushen daro asi paxides
\p 
\v 12 Hawaaretikka dere giddon daro malatanne malalisiza miish ooththida. Ammanizayti wuri “Solomoone simeretethaso” geetettiza pengen shiiqeetes.
\v 13 Istas babbida gish oonnikka istara walakketanas koyibenna. Gido attin derey ista keehi bonches.
\v 14 Daro macasattinne addeti wodeppe woden Godan ammani ammani ista bolla gujettida.
\v 15 Hessa gaason Phexroosi aadhdhishin haray attin iza eeshoy harganchatappe bagga harganchata bolla wodhdhana mala hargizayti ichchiza alga bollanne hala bolla karen ishiseetes.
\v 16 Yerusalame yuushon diza katamatappe hargizaytanne tuna ayanay waayssizayta ehin wuri paxida.
\s1 Hawaareta bolla gakkida goodeteththinne waaye
\p 
\v 17 Hessa wode Qeeseta Halaqaynne izara diza Saduqaaweta baggati wurikka qanate qanatizayta xalla gidida.
\v 18 Hawaareta oykkidi qasho keeththe gelthida.
\v 19 Gido attin Goda kiitanchay qamara qasho keeththa kare doyidi ista kessidi,
\v 20 “Biidi Xoossa Keeththa gibbe giddon eqqidi hayssa de7o qaala ubba deres yootite” gides.
\p 
\v 21 Gadey wontida mala istas yootidayssa Xoossa Keeththa gibbe gelidi dereza tamarso oykkida; Qeeseta halaqaynne izara dizayti yiidi Ayhudata duulatanne Isra7eele dere cimata kumeth issi bolla shiishida. Hawaareta qasho keeththafe ekki yaana mala as yeddida.
\v 22 Kiiteti bida asati biidi ista qasho keeththan demmibeetenna; simmidinne
\v 23 “Qasho keeththay lo7ethi qulfeti dees; naagizaytikka penge bolla eqqi dishin beyidos; gido attin nu doy gelishin qas keeththan oonikka ba” gida.
\v 24 Xoossa Keeththi naagizayta halaqaynne Qeeseta Halaqatika hessa siyida mala hanozan daro malaletidanne istas hanoy wuri tikki gides.
\v 25 Heerakka issi asi yiidi “Hekko inte qasho keeththe gelthida asati Xoossa Keeththa gibbe giddon eqqidi dere tamarson deettes” gides.
\v 26 Xoossa Keeththe naagizayta halaqay ba oosanchatara biidi ista oykki ekki yides. Oykki ehidaytti asay bana shuchchara caddonta mala babbidi wolqathonta loddara ehida.
\p 
\v 27-28 Hawaareta ehidi Ayhuda duulata sinthan essida. Qeeseta halaqaykka ista “Hayssa ha sunthan inte tamarsonta mala intes lo7ethi yootidoskoshin inte inte timirteza Yerusalame ubban kuntheta. Qasse nunakka ha addeza suuthas oyshetizayta histanas gixxi dendideta” gides. \x * \xo 5:27-28 \xt Mato 27:25\x*
\p 
\v 29 Phexroosinne hanko Hawaaretikka zaaridi “Nuni asappe aaththidi Xoossas azazettanas bessees.
\p 
\v 30 “Inte iza mitha bolla kaqqi wodhida Yesusa nu aawanta Xoossay iza hayqoppe denthides.
\v 31 Izikka Isra7eele naytas nagarappe simmidi maarettana mala Xoossi iza ubbafe bollanne ashshizade histidi ba ushachchan dhoqu dhoqu histides.
\v 32 Nunikka hayssas markata. Qasseka Xoossi baas azazettiza oonaska immida Xillo Ayanaykka marka” gida.
\p 
\v 33 Asati hessa siydi iita hanqo hanqettida. Wodhanakka koyda.
\v 34 Gido attin dere achchan keehi bonchettida issi woga astamare, izikka Gamalyaale geetettiza Farsaaweeta baggay dere cimata giddon dendi eqqidi Hawaareti guuththa wode karen gam7ana mala azazides.
\v 35 Dere cimatas hizgides “Isra7eele asato! Inte hayta asata bolla ooththanayssa daro akeekkara ooththanas bessees.
\v 36 Hayssafe kase issi Tewoodaasa geetettizadey bana gita as histi qoodi dendin oyddu xeetu derey iza kaallides. Gido attin izi asa kushen hayqqides. Iza kaallizaytikka coo laalettin iza hanoy coo mela attides.
\v 37 Izappe guyekka derey taybetiza wode Galila Yuhuday dendidi daro dere banara kaalethides. Bana kaallizaytaka demmides shin izikka dhayides. Iza kaallizaytikka wuri dhayida.
\p 
\v 38 “Hessa gish ta ha7i intena gizay hayta asata aggite, bochchofte. Ista qofay woykko ista oosoy asappe gidikko dhayana.
\v 39 Xoossafe gidikko qas inte ista teqanas dandayekketa. Oone erizay inte Xoossara oyeetishe beettanakkonne” gides.
\p 
\v 40 Istika iza zoreza ekkidi Hawaareta xeygidi garafissida. Nam7antho Yesusa sunthan haasayonta mala azazidi yeddida.
\v 41 Hawaaretikka iza suntha gish kawuyanas bessiza gish daro ufayetishe dere cimata achchafe kezi bida.
\v 42 Gallas gallas Xoossa Keeththaninne issa issa keeththan Yesusi izi Xoossi dooridade gididayssa tamarsofenne sabakoppe mulekka guye gibeetenna.
\c 6
\s1 Laapun daaqoneta dooreteth
\p 
\v 1 Ammanizayta qooday dari dari biza wode Girike biittafe yida Ayhuda asati Yuhudan diza Ayhuda asa guyera zigirettida. Gaasoyka ubba wode miza kath gishishe am7eta wudetonta aggida gishassa.
\v 2 Hessa gish nu tammanne nam7u Hawaareti ammaniza harata issi bolla shiishshidi “Nuni kaththa gishon gelidi Xoossa qaala tamarso agganas bessenna.
\v 3 Hessa gish nu ishato! Inte giddofe eranchata, Xillo Ayanan kumidaytanne lo7o markateth diza laapun asata doorite; hayssa alafeteth nu istas immana.
\v 4 Nuni gidikko woossaninne qaala yooton minnana” gida.
\p 
\v 5 Isti gida yo7oy siyidayta ufaysides; Ammanoninne Xillo Ayanan kumidayti Istifanoose, Piliphoosa, Phirosqoroosa, Niqaroona, Ximoona, Pharmenanne Yuhudatethan gelida Anxokiya dere as Niqoloosa doorida.
\v 6 Heyta ehidi Hawaareta sinth shiishida. Istika ba kushe ista bolla woththidi istas woossida.
\p 
\v 7 Xoossa qaalay akki akki bides. Ammanizayta qooday Yerusalamen dari dari bides. Qeesetappe daroti ammanida.
\s1 Istifanoose oyketeth
\p 
\v 8 He wode Istifanoossi Xoossa immotethaninne wolqan kumidi dereza giddon gita malalisiza malatata ooththides.
\v 9 Wozeti kezida geetetti xeeygetizasoppe Ayhudata Woosa Keeththafe yida as gidida Qareenappenne Iskindiriyappe; qasseka Kilqiyappenne Iisiya awurajjatappe yida asatikka wuri Istifanoosera marshetida.
\v 10 Gido attin eratethan izi haasayiza haasayanne izan diza Ayana eqqetanas dandayibeetenna.
\v 11 Hessa gish “Istifanoossi Musenne Xoosse cayishin nu siyidos” giza asata guyera giigissida.
\p 
\v 12 He wode dereza, dere cimatanne woga tamarsizayta dentheththidine Istifanoose oythidi dere duulatakko shiishida.
\v 13 Iza bolla “Hayssi addezi hayssa Xoossa Keeththa bollanne woga bolla cashsha qaala haasaya mulekka aggibenna.
\v 14 Gaasoyka hayssi addezi ‘Naazirete Yesusi hayssa Xoossa Keeththa dhayssana’ gishininne ‘Nu Museppe ekkida woga laammana’ gi haasayishin nu siyidos” gi wordora markattiza asata shiishshidi markasida.
\p 
\v 15 Duulata uttida asay wuri Istifanoose tishshi histi xeellishin iza ayfesoy istas kiitancha ayfeso misati beettides.
\c 7
\p 
\v 1 Qeeseta halaqay Istifanoose “Hayssi ne bolla shiiqida yo7ozi tumee?” gi oychides.
\p 
\v 2 Istifanoossika hizgides “Ta ishato! Ta aawato! Ta gizayssa siyite! Nu aawa Abrahaamey Kaarane geetettizaso yaanappe kase buro Mesopotoomiyan dishin boncho Goday izas qoncidi,
\v 3 ‘Ne dereppenne ne dabbofe shaaketada ta nena bessizaso ba’ gides.
\v 4 Izikka Kaldaweta biittafe kezidi Kaarane geetettiza biittan uttides. Iza aaway hayqqidappe guye inte ha7i dizaso ha dere iza ehides. \x * \xo 7:4 \xt Medhe 11:31; 12:4\x*
\v 5 Haray attoshin issi tohoy eqqiza gadey izas hayssafe immetibenna. Gido attin he wode izas issi naykka baynda dishin izinne izappe guyen iza zerethi Biittayo laattana mala Xoossi izas caqqides. \x * \xo 7:5 \xt Medhe 12:7; 13:15; 15:18; 17:8\x*
\v 6 Qasseka Xoossi izas hizgi yootides ‘Ne zerethi allaga biittan bete as gidana. Oyddu xeetu layth aylletetha qambara giddon waayettana. \x * \xo 7:6 \xt Medhe 15:13-14\x*
\v 7 Gido attin ista aylle mala haariza dere ta qaxayana. Hessafe guye isti he biittafe kezidi hanno ha soyn taas goynnana’ gides. \x * \xo 7:7 \xt Kessa 3:12\x*
\v 8 Hessafe guye qaxxara woga caaqo izas immides. Abrahaameyka Yisaaqa yelidi iza ospuntha gallas qaxxarides. Yisaaqaykka Yaqoobe yelides. Yaqoobeykka tammanne nam7u qommota yelides. \x * \xo 7:8 \xt Medhe 17:10-14; 21:2-4; 25:26; 29:31-35:18\x*
\p 
\v 9 “He qommota aawati Yoosefe bolla qanatidi iza aylletethas duge Gibxe bayzida. Gido attin Xoossi izara dees; \x * \xo 7:9 \xt Medhe 37:11; 37:28; 39:2,21\x*
\v 10 meto ubbafe iza ashshides. Gibxe kawo Paaroone sinthan boncho immides. Paarooney iza Gibxe biittaninne ba keeththa asa ubba bolla alafetethan shuumides. \x * \xo 7:10 \xt Medhe 41:39-41\x*
\p 
\v 11 “He wode Kanaaneninne Gibxen daro meto ehida gita koshay dendides. Nu aawataska miza kaththi dhayides. \x * \xo 7:11 \xt Medhe 42:1-2\x*
\v 12 Yaqoobey Gibxe deren kaththi dizayssa siydi nu aawata koyro Gibxe yeddides.
\v 13 Isti nam7antho biza wode Yoosefey izi oonakkonne bana ba ishatas qoncisides. Paarooneykka Yoosefe ishata erides. \x * \xo 7:13 \xt Medhe 45:1; 45:16\x*
\v 14 Hessafe guye Yoosefey kiittidi ba aawa Yaqoobenne laapun tammanne ichashu gidiza ba dabbota kumeth ehisides. \x * \xo 7:14 \xt Medhe 45:9-10,17-18; 46:27\x*
\v 15 Yaqoobey duge Gibxe wodhdhides. Izikka nu aawatikka wuri heen hayqqida. \x * \xo 7:15 \xt Medhe 46:1-7; 49:33\x*
\v 16 Ista ahaykka Seekeme geetettizaso efin Abrahaamey Eemoore naytappe ba miishan shammida duufon moogetides. \x * \xo 7:16 \xt Medhe 23:3-16; 33:19; 50:7-13; Iya 24:32\x*
\p 
\v 17 “Xoossi Abrahaames caaqida qaalay poletiza wodey matishin Gibxen diza nu asa qooday dari dari bides.
\v 18 Hessafe guye Gibxe biittan Yoosefe eronta hara kawoy kawotides.
\v 19 Izikka nu asa ba gene ooson metothides. Buro yelettida guutha nayti hayqqana malanne yelida nayta kare kessi wora yeggana mala wolqathides. \x * \xo 7:19 \xt Kessa 1:10-11; 1:22\x*
\v 20 He wode Musey yeletides. Izikka Xoossa achchan dosettida mala lo7o naa gidides. Ba aawa keeththan heedzdzu agina al7isson diccides. \x * \xo 7:20 \xt Kessa 2:2\x*
\v 21 Izi gede wora yegetida wode kawo Paaroone maca naya demmada baas ekkadus. Ba naa mala ooththada dichchadus. \x * \xo 7:21 \xt Kessa 2:3-10\x*
\v 22 Museykka Gibxeta aadhdho eratetha wursi tamarides. Yo7on era; oosonka mino gidides.
\p 
\v 23 “Muse laythi oyddu tammu gidida wode Musey ba ishata Isra7eele nayta beyanas ba woznan qoppides. \x * \xo 7:23 \xt Kessa 2:11-15\x*
\v 24 Izikka issi Gibxe asi Muse bagga asappe issade bolla qoho gaththishin beyidi ba bagga addeza maadides; he Gibxe addeza wodhidi he qohetidayssa halo kessides.
\v 25 Muses Xoossi iza kushen ista wozanayssa iza asay akeekkiza misatides. Gido attin isti hessa yuushi qoppibetenna.
\v 26 Wontetha gallas qasseka Isra7eele naytappe nam7ati ba giddon oyeetishin gakkidi oyeetizayta giigissanas koydi ‘Hayto! Asato inte inte giddon ishantakko; inte waanidi issoy issa qoheetii?’ gides.
\p 
\v 27-28 “Ba laggeza bolla qoho gaththidayssi Muse sugi yeggidi ‘Nena nu bolla nuna haarizadenne nu bolla pirdizade ooththi shuumiday oonee? Woykko qamma Gibxe addeza wodhoyssatho tanakka wodhana koyay?’ gides.
\v 29 Musey hessa siyida mala Midiyaame biitta beettidi heen bete as gidi de7ides; Yaanka nam7u attuma naa yelides. \x * \xo 7:29 \xt Kessa 18:3-4\x*
\p 
\v 30 “Hessafe oyddu tammu laythafe guye Siina zuma achchan diza bazzo biittan qeeri wora giddon eexiza tama lacon kiitanchay izas beettides.
\v 31-32 Museykka iza beyida mala malaletides. Azakkonne shaakki eranas izi heen izakko shiiqishin Goda qaalay ‘Tani ne aawanta Xoossa Abrahaame, Yisaaqanne Yaqoobe Xoossa’ gishin siydes. Museykka daro daggamides; xeellanaska xalibenna.
\p 
\v 33-34 “Godayka izas ‘Hayssi ne eqqidasoy geeshshaso gidida gish ne tohoppe caamma shodda. Gibxen diza ta dereta waaye ta tumappe beyadis; isti waassiza waaye waasoza ta siyada ista ashshanas wodhdhadis. Ne ha7ikka haaya; ta nena duge Gibxe zaarada kiitana’ gides.
\p 
\v 35 “Histin heyti ‘Nu bolla nena haarizadenne pirdizade histi ooni shuumidee?’ giidi asay kase kadhida Muse Xoossi qeeri wora giddon izas bettida kiitancha baggara ista haarizadenne ashshizade histidi istako zaari yeddides.
\v 36 Izikka ista kaalethidi Gibxeppe kessides. Gibxen, Zo7o Abbaninne bazzo biittan oyddu tammu laythi daro malalisiza miishatanne gita malatata istas ooththides. \x * \xo 7:36 \xt Kessa 7:3; 14:21; Tay 14:33\x*
\v 37 “Isra7eele naytas ‘Ta mala nabe Xoossi inte giddofe denthana’ gidayssi hayssa Musekko! \x * \xo 7:37 \xt Zaare 18:15,18\x*
\v 38 Izikka Siina zuma bolla haasayida kiitancharanne bazzo biittan nu aawatara dere duulata giddon dees. De7o qaalakka ha nuus aaththanas ekkides. \x * \xo 7:38 \xt Kessa 19:1-20:17; Zaare 5:1-33\x*
\p 
\v 39 “Nu Aawati gidikko izara eqqetida attin izas azazettanas koyonta gish ba woznara guye Gibxe simmida.
\v 40 Aaroneska ‘Nu sinthara biza eeqa nuus giigissa! Nuna Gibxeppe kaalethi kessida Musey waanidakko nu erokko’ gida. \x * \xo 7:40 \xt Kessa 32:1\x*
\v 41 He wode mara misile medhidi eeqas yarsho shiishida. Barka medhdhida ba kushe ooson ufayetidi guppida. \x * \xo 7:41 \xt Kessa 32:2-6\x*
\p 
\v 42 “Gido attin Xoossi istas zokko zaarides. Isti salo xoolintetas goynnana mala aaththi immides. Hessika nabeta maxaafan
\q2 ‘Inteno Isra7eele nayto!
\q3 Inte bazzo biittan oyddu tammu layth diza wode intefe yarshonne muxuwata taas shiishshi eretii?
\q1 
\v 43 Harappeka inte goynnanaso ooththida eeqa Molooke dunkananne
\q3 inte eeqa Rafaanne xoolinte misileza dhoqu dhoqu histi oykkideta.
\q2 Hessa gish ta intena inte dizasoppe denthada Babiloonera aaththa yeddana’
\q2 geetettidi xaafettides.
\p 
\v 44 “Xoossi Muse bessida leemisoza malanne azazidayssa mala oosettida Xoossi asara gaaggiza dunkaneya nu aawatara bazzo biittan de7adus. \x * \xo 7:44 \xt Kessa 25:9,40\x*
\v 45 Nu Aawati dunkaneyo ekkidayssafe guye Xoossi Iyaaso kaaleththin kase ista gooddida dereta laattida wode dunkaneyo ekki geellida. Dawute wode gakkanaas dunkaneya he biittan de7adus. \x * \xo 7:45 \xt Iya 3:14-17\x*
\v 46 Dawuteykka Xoossa sinthan boncho demmidi Yaqoobe Godas aqoso giigissanas woossides. \x * \xo 7:46 \xt 2Same 7:1-16; 1Taar 17:1-14\x*
\v 47 Gido attin Solomooney izas aqqoso keexxides.
\p 
\v 48-50 “Gido attin wogga Goday asa kushey keexida keeththan deenna. Hessika nabey
\q3 kase Geeshsha maxaafan xaafetida mala
\q2 ‘Saloy ta uttiza alga;
\q3 biittaykka ta tohon yedhdhizaso;
\q2 histin inte taas ay mala keeththe keexxetii?
\q3 woykko ta shempanasoy awayssee? \x * \xo 7:48-50 \xt Isa 66:1-2\x*
\q2 Hayssa wursi ta kushey ooththibenee?’
\q3 gees Goday Xoossay.
\p 
\v 51 “Inteno wozna muumeto! Haytha tulleto! Inteka inte aawata mala ubba wode Xillo Ayanara eqetteta. \x * \xo 7:51 \xt Isa 63:10\x*
\v 52 Nabetappe inte Aawati gooddonta nabey oonee? Xilloza Yohannisa kaseti yootida nabetaka wodhida; inteka ha7i iza aaththi immidetanne wodhideta.
\v 53 Kiitancha baggara intes imettida woga ekkideta attin naagibeekketa” gides.
\s1 Istifanoossi shuchchan cadeti hayqqides
\p 
\v 54 Duulatan diza asay hessa siyida mala daro hanqettidi, iza bolla ba achchi garcides.
\v 55-56 Gidinka Istifanoosi Xillo Ayanan kumidinne pude salo tishshi histi xeellishin Xoossa bonchon Yesusi Xoossa ushachchan eqqidayssa beyidi “Hekko ta saloy doyettidayssanne Asa Nay Xoossa ushachchan eqqidayssa beyays” gides.
\p 
\v 57 Hessa wode asay qaala dhoqu histi waassishe ba haythe tucci oykidi izakko issife woxxides.
\v 58 Istifanoose oykkidi katamappe gede kare olida. Shuchchan cach oykkida. Hessi wuri hanishin markatikka ba may7o Sawule geetettiza paantha achchan woththida.
\v 59 Isti shuchchara iza caddishin Istifanoossi “Ta Goda Yesusaa ta shempoyo neekko ekka” giidi woossides.
\v 60 Qasseka gulbatidi dhoqa qaalan “Godo! Haytanta nagara qoodoppa” giidi waassides. Hessa gidappe guye hayqqides.
\c 8
\p 
\v 1 Sawuleykka Istifanoose hayqon istara qofan gaaggides. He wode Yerusalamen diza ammanizayta bolla gita goodeteththi dendides. Hawaareti attaafe ammanizayti wuri Yuhuda awurajjaninne Samaariya awurajjan ubban laalettida.
\v 2 Ayana ooson minni eqqida asati Istifanoose moogidi, izas daro yeekkida.
\v 3 Sawuley qasse Woosa Keeththa dhayssanas gixxi dendides. Ammaniza asa issa issa keeththe gelidi macatanne addeta goochchi goochchi kessidi qasho keeththan gelthides. \x * \xo 8:3 \xt Hawa 22:4-5; 26:9-11\x*
\s1 Piliphoosi Samaariya deren Mishiraachcho qaala markattides
\p 
\v 4 Laalettidayti wuri ba bidason bidason Xoossa qaala yootida.
\v 5 Piliphoosikka Samaariya geetettiza katama wodhdhidi asas Kirstoosa sabakides.
\v 6 Daro derey Piliphoosi ooththiza malata beyidi izi yootiza qaala woznappe lo7ethi siydes.
\v 7 Tuna ayanatikka daro asappe waassi waassi kezida. Daro toho silatinne wobetikka paxida.
\v 8 Hessa gish he katama asay daro ufayetides.
\p 
\v 9 Gido attin hessafe kase he katamayin maro marotidi Samaariya asa daro malalisizaz ooththiza issi Simoona geetettiza maroy dees. Izikka bana gita asa mala qoodizade.
\v 10 Asay wuri guuthatappe gitata gakkanaas wurikka “Hayssi addezi gita wolqama geetettiza Xoossa wolqa” gishe izi gizayssa wursi woznappe siyees.
\v 11 Daro wode ba marotetha ooson asa malalisida gish asay iza woznappe kaallishe gam7ides.
\v 12 Gido attin Piliphoosi Xoossa Kawoteththa gishshinne Yesus Kirstoosa gish sabakidayssa siydi ammanida macasaynne attumasay xammaqetides.
\v 13 Simoonikka ammanidi xammaqetides. Piliphoosakka kaalli biidi haniza gita malata beyidi malalettides.
\p 
\v 14 Yerusalamen diza Hawaareti Samaariya asay Xoossa qaala ekkidi ammanidayssa siydi Phexroosanne Yohannisa Istako kiittida.
\v 15 Istika Samaariya gakkidi ammanida asay Xillo Ayana ekkana mala asas woossida.
\v 16 Gaasoyka he wode isti coo Yesusa sunthan xammaqetida attin buro Xillo Ayanay istafe issade bollakka wodhdhibenna.
\v 17 Hessa gish Phexroosinne Yohannisi ba kushe asa bolla woththin asay Xillo Ayana ekkides.
\p 
\v 18 Simoonikka Hawaareti kushe woththi woossin Xillo Ayanay imettizayssa beyidi Phexroosasinne Yohannisas miishe ekki yiidi,
\v 19 “Ta iza bolla ta kushe woththizadey wuri Xillo Ayana ekkana mala hayssa mala godateth taaska immite” giin,
\p 
\v 20 Phexroosi izas zaaridi “Xoossa imota ne miishan shammana qoppida gish neni ne miishara issife dhaya.
\v 21 Ne woznay Xoossa sinthan suure gidonta gish nees hayssa ha oosozan gishay woykko qaaday deenna.
\v 22 Hayssa ne iitatetha gish ha7i elle maarotethan gela; ne wozna qofa nees atto gaanakkonne nees Goda woossa.
\v 23 Gaasoyka neni iitatethan kumidayssinne makalan qasheta uttidayssi taas beettees” gides.
\p 
\v 24 Simoonikka zaaridi “Inte gida yo7otappe aykkoykka ta bolla gakkonta mala taas Goda woossite” gides.
\p 
\v 25 Phexroosinne Yohannisi Goda qaala markattidayssafenne qoncisi yootidayssafe guye daro Samaariya gutatan mishiraachcho qaala sabakishe Yerusalame simmida.
\s1 Tophiya kawo miisha bolla shuumetida gundulaza Piliphoosi xammaqides
\p 
\v 26 Goda kiitanchay Piliphoosa “Denda! Yerusalameppe duge baggara gede Gaaza efiza bazzo ogara ba” gides.
\v 27 Izikka dendi bides. Hindeko geetettiza Tophiyappe gidida kawoya ba keeththaninne ba kawoteththan diza ubba miisha bolla alafetethan woththida issi Tophiya gundula asi izara gaaggides. He addezi Xoossas goynnana Yerusalame bides.
\v 28 Izi heeppe simmishe para-gaaren uttidi nabe Isayaasa maxaafa nababes.
\v 29 Ayanay Piliphoosa “Ba! Gede para-gaarezakko shiiqa” gides.
\p 
\v 30 Piliphoosikka eesotidi para-gaarezakko biidi addezi nabe Isayaasa maxaafa nababishin siydi “Hessi ne nababizayssi nees gelizee?” gides.
\p 
\v 31 Gundula addezikka “Tana erisiza asi baynda ta wosta eroo?” gides. Izikka gede iza gaarezan geldi iza achchan uttana mala woossides.
\v 32 Izi nababiza maxaafay
\q2 “Izi dorsa mala shukettana laagettides;
\q3 dorsa laaqay isike qanxizayssa sinthan co7u giza mala
\q3 hessathoka izi ba duuna pogibenna.
\q1 
\v 33 Bana kawushshidi pirday bayndade gidides.
\q3 Iza shempoy biitta bollafe diggettides.
\q3 Iza yeletetha gish haasayana dandayizay oonee?” gees.
\p 
\v 34 Gundula addezikka zaaridi Piliphoosa “Nabezi hayssa oona gish gizee? Ba gish gizeyee? Woykko hara asa gish gizee? Hayana, taas yootarki!” gides.
\v 35 Piliphoosikka ba duuna doydi he maxaafappe doommidi Yesusa Mishiraachcho qaala gish markattides.
\p 
\v 36 Isti issife bishe haaththi dizaso gakkida. Addezikka “Hekko haaththi hayssan dees; histin ta xammaqetonta mala diggizay aazee?” gides.
\p 
\v 37 Piliphoosikka “Ne kumeththa woznappe ammanikko xammaqettana dandayassa” gides. Addezikka “Yesus Kirstoosi Xoossa Naa gididayssa ammanays” gides. \f + \fr 8:37 \ft Issi issi Geeshsha Maxaafati paydo 37 bolla diza qofa gujjetes; issi issoti qasseka qofa oykkibetenna.\f*
\p 
\v 38 Addezi para gaarezi eqqana mala azazin nam7ay issife haaththan wodhdhin Piliphoosi addeza xammaqides.
\v 39 Isti haaththafe kezishin Xoossa Ayanay Piliphoosa denthi efides. Addezi hessafe guye iza beybenna. Gido attin ufayssan ba oge bides.
\v 40 Hessafe guye Piliphoosi Azaxoone geetettizason beettides. Qisaariya geetettizaso gakkanaas izi biza oge bolla kataman ubban mishiraachcho qaala sabakides.
\c 9
\s1 Sawuley ammanides
\r (Hawa 22:6-16; 26:12-18)
\p 
\v 1 Sawuley Goda ammaniza asa wodhanas ceeqqettishe Qeeseta halaqakko bides.
\v 2 Goda oge kaallizayta macasatanne addeta demmi qachidi Yerusalame ekki yaanas Damasqo geetettizason diza Ayhudata Woosa Keeththas babdaabe xaafana mala Qeeseta halaqa woossides.
\p 
\v 3 Damasqo gakkana matishin qopponta saloppe poo7oy iza yuushon pol7u gides.
\v 4 Izikka heerakka biitta bolla kundidi saloppe “Sawule, Sawule, tana aazas goodday?” giza qaala siydes.
\p 
\v 5 Sawuleyka “Godo! Ne oonee?” gides. Izikka izas “Tani ne goodeththiza Yesusakko!” \f + \fr 9:5 \ft Issi issi Geeshsha Maxaafata birsheththay “Qara mashsha bolla ne eqqikko qohettana” gishin harayti qas “Caddiza biratara ne eqqetikko nees ha darana” geetes.\f*\f + \fr 9:5 \ft Sawuli kokkordinne yashshatethan malaletidi “Godo! Ta nees ay ooththana mala dosay?” gides giza qofa gujjetes. Hayssaka shempo 22:10 nne 26:14 bolla xaafeti beettes.\f*
\v 6 “Ne ha7i dendada gede katama gela; ne ooththanas bessizaz nees ta yootana” gides.
\p 
\v 7 Sawulera issife biza asati qaala giiris sissafe attin oonakka beyonta gish ba duuna oykki eqqida.
\v 8 Sawuley ba kundidasoppe dendidi ayfe doyi xeelliza wode aykkokka demmanas dandaybenna. Hessa gish izara diza asati iza kushe oykkidi kaalethi ekkidi Damasqo efida.
\v 9 Heedzdzu gallas gakkanaas qooqidinne kath haaththe beybenna.
\p 
\v 10 Damasqon issi Hananiya geetettiza ammanizadey dees. Izas Goday ajjutan “Hananiya” giidi xeygides; izikka “Yee Godo!” gides.
\p 
\v 11 Godayka iza “Denda! Suure geetettiza ogeyra Yuhuda geetettizaso ba. Heen Sawule geetettiza issi Xarseese asi woossishe dees; ne iza koya demma.
\v 12 Gaasoyka Hananiya geetettizayssi Sawuley dizaso yiidi izi xeellana mala iza bolla ba kushe woththishin ajjutan beyides.”
\p 
\v 13 Hananiyaykka zaaridi “Godo! Hayssadey Yerusalamen diza geeshshata bolla ay mala iita meto gaththidakkonne ta daro asappe siyadis.
\v 14 Izi haa yiday ne suntha xeygizayta wursi qachanas Qeeseta halaqatappe godateth ekkidikko” gides.
\p 
\v 15 Godayka izas “Ne ba! Hayssi addezi Ayzaabeta sinthaninne kawota sinthan hessathoka Isra7eele dere sinthan ta sunth tookkana mala izi taas doorettidayssa.
\v 16 Izi ta suntha gish ay mala waaye beyanakko ta iza bessana” gides.
\p 
\v 17 Hananiyay biidi izas yootetidaso gelides. Sawule bolla ba kushe woththidi “Ta isha Sawule ne ha yishin nees oge bolla qoncida Goda Yesusi ne ayfey xeellana malanne neni Xillo Ayanan kumana mala tana neekko kiittides” gides.
\v 18 Heerakka Sawule ayfeppe poqo malay poqeti wodhdhin izi xeellana dandayidessinne dendidi xammaqetides.
\v 19 Kaththikka miidi minnides. Undena wode ammanizaytara Damasqon gam7ides.
\s1 Sawuley Damasqoninne Yerusalamen tamarsides
\p 
\v 20 Heerakka Yesusi Xoossa Naa gididayssa Ayhudata Woosa Keeththatan tamarso oykkides.
\p 
\v 21 Siyida asay wuri “Hayssi Yerusalamen ha suntha xeygizayta dhayissiza addeza gidenee? Qasse izi ha yiday he asata qachi ekki Qeeseta Halaqatakko efanas deenee?” gishe malaletida.
\p 
\v 22 Sawuley kaseppe minni minni bides. Damasqon diza Ayhudatas Yesusi izi Xoossi kiittidade gididayssa ammanthishe asa duuna oythides.
\p 
\v 23 Daro gallassatappe guye Ayhudati Sawule wodhanas duulatida. \x * \xo 9:23 \xt 2Qoro 11:32-33\x*
\v 24 Izikka ista qofa erides. Istika iza wodhanas katama gelthiza ogen gallassinne qamma naagida.
\v 25 Ammanizayti gidikko iza gidoth katama yuushon diza maskotezara keeshen duge woththida.
\p 
\v 26 Sawuley Yerusalame yiidi ammanizaytara walakkettana koyin izi tumu ammanizade gididayssa isti ammanetonta gish izas babbida.
\v 27 Gido attin Barnabaassi iza Hawaaretakko efin Sawuley izi Damasqo oge bolla Goda wosti beyidakko, Godayka izas ay yootidakkonne qasseka Damasqon dishe izi ay mala xalateththara Yesusa sunthan sabakidakko istas yootides.
\p 
\v 28 Hessa gish Sawuley istara dides. Yerusalamen yuuyi yuuyi as babbonta Goda sunthan tamarsides.
\v 29 Girike dereppe yida Ayhudatara haasayshe palametides; gido attin asaykka iza wodhanas koyides.
\v 30 Ammanizayti hessa eridi duge Qisaariya geetettizaso woththidi Xarseese yeddida.
\p 
\v 31 Hessa wode Yuhudaninne Galilan, Samaariyanka diza ammanizayti saron diidi kaseppe minnida. Qasseka Xoossa yashshatethan simeretishe Xillo Ayanan minetidanne kaseppe qoodan dari dari bida.
\s1 Eeniyanne Dorqa
\p 
\v 32 Phexroosi dereppe deren yuuyishe Liida kataman diza ammanizayta beyanas duge wodhdhides.
\v 33 Heen Eniya geetettizayssa osupun layth hiixan qasheti uttida issi gunda as demmides.
\v 34 Phexroosikka “Haysso Eniya! Yesus Kirstoosi nena pathana; denda ne hiixa dentha!” gides. Eniyay heerakka pusuku gi dendides.
\v 35 Liidaninne Saroonan diza asay wuri iza beyidi Godan ammanides.
\p 
\v 36 Iyophphe geetettizason Xaabita geetettiza issi ammanizara dawus. Izi suntha birsheththi Girike qaalara “Dorqa” geetettes. Iza ubba wode lo7o ooso minna ooththashenne manqota maaddashe dawus. \f + \fr 9:36 \fk Dorqa \ft Hessa guussi Girike qaalara “Genessa guussa”\f*
\v 37 He wode iza hargada hayqqin asay aha meeci pude pooqen kessi woththides.
\v 38 Liiday Iyophphes mata gidida gish ammanizayti Phexroosi Liidan dizayssa siydi nam7u asata kiittidi “Elle ha yarki!” gi woossida.
\p 
\v 39 Phexroosikka dendidi kiitettida asatara gakkida wode iza pude he pooqe bolla kessida. Am7etikka wuri iza yuuyi aadhdhi eqqidi Dorqay paxa dashe istara ooththida qamisetanne may7ota bessishe yeekkida.
\p 
\v 40 Phexroosikka asa wursi kiflezappe kessidi gulbati woossides. Ahakko simmidi “Hanne Xaabita denda!” gides. Izakka ba ayfe doyada xeelladus. Phexroosakka beyada denda uttadus.
\v 41 Izikka izi kushe oykki denthides. Ammanizaytanne am7eta xeygidi izo istas pathidi immides.
\v 42 He hanoy kumeththa Iyophphen eretidesinne daro asayka Goda ammanides.
\v 43 Phexroosikka issi Simoona geetettiza galba qaacizadera Iyophphen daro wode de7ides.
\c 10
\s1 Qornoloosi Phexroosa xeygisides
\p 
\v 1 Qisaariya geetettiza deren “Xaalane wotadarata” issi butte giddon mato halaqa gidida issi Qornoloosa geetettizayssi dees.
\v 2 Izikka ba keeththa asa kumeththara Ayana hanon minonne Xoosse babbizadde; manqotaska daro muxuwata immizadenne daro wode Xoosse woossiza asa.
\v 3 Issi gallas gallassafe uddufun saate bolla Xoossa kiitanchay izas ajjutan beettidi izakko yiidi “Qornoloosa” gi xeygishin qoncen beyides.
\p 
\v 4 Qornoloosikka dagamara tishshi histi xeellishe “Godo hayssi aazee?” gides. Kiitanchaykka zaaridi “Ne woossaynne ne muxuwatay qofetanas pude Xoossa sinth gakkides.
\v 5 Ne ha7i as Iyophphe yedada Phexroosa geetettiza Simoona xeygisa.
\v 6 Izikka abba matan diza galba qaaciza Simoona soon imathateth dees” gides.
\p 
\v 7 Qornoloosa haasayssida kiitanchay izappe shaaketidi bidappe guye ba ashkaratappe nam7ata qasse Ayana yo7os minone izas daro ammanettiza wotadaratappe issa xeygisidi,
\v 8 izi beyidayssa wursi istas yootidi Iyophphe kiittides.
\s1 Phexroosi beyida ajjuta
\p 
\v 9 Kiitettida asati wontetha gallas gede katamaykko matishin Phexroosi usuppun saate bolla woossana pude Pooqe bolla kezides.
\v 10-11 Hessa wode izi gafida gish qumay buro kaxxishin dhisko mala liphiphi histin ajjutara saloy doyettin issi gita xaaxettida may7o malay oyddu baggara oyketidi duge biittan wodhdhishin beyides.
\v 12 He may7oza bolla oyddu tohoy diza dumma dumma do7ati biittara gooshettiza medhetethatinne salo bolla piradhiza kafoti deettes.
\v 13 Hessa wode “Phexroosa denda hayta shukada ma” giza qaalay izas siyetides.
\p 
\v 14 Phexroosi qasse “Godo hayssi hanenna! Geesh gidontayssa woykko tuna miisha ta mulerakka ma erikke” gides.
\p 
\v 15 He kase qaalay qasseka nam7antho izakko yiidi “Xoossi geeshshidayssa ne tuna mala qoodoppa” gides.
\v 16 Hessika heedzdzuto shireti shireti izakko yidappe guye may7o misatizayssi heerakka pude salo bides.
\p 
\v 17 Phexroosikka ba beyida ajjutaza birsheththa eranas daro metotidi keehi qofo bolla dishin Qornoloosi kiittida asati Simoona keeththe koyishe demmidi pengen eqqida.
\v 18 Qaala dhoqu histidi “Phexroosa geetettiza Simooni dizasoy hayssan awanee?” gi oychida.
\p 
\v 19-20 Phexroosi ba beyidayssa keehi qoppishin Xillo Ayanay iza “Hekko heedzdzu asati nena koyeetes. Denda! Duge wodhdhada ista yeddiday tana gidida gish sidhey baynda istara ba” gides.
\p 
\v 21 Phexroosikka duge wodhdhidi “Hekko inte koyizadey tanakko! Inte yiday aazasee?” gides.
\v 22 Istika izas “Nuni mato halaqa Qornoloosa matappe yidos. Izikka Xoossas babbiza xillo asanne Ayhuda asa ubba matan daro bonchettida asa. Nekka iza keeththe baana malanne ne gizayssa izi siyana mala geeshsha kiitanchay izas yootides” gida.
\p 
\v 23 Phexroosikka asata ba dizason mokki ekkidi ayssides.
\s1 Phexroosi Qornoloosa keeththan
\p Phexroosikka wontetha gallas dendidi istara bides. Iyophphefe yida issi issi ammaniza asati izara issife bida.
\v 24 Qornoloosikka ba dabbotanne mata laggeta ba soon shiishshidi naago bolla dishin izi nam7antho gallas Qisaariya gakkides.
\v 25 Phexroosikka gede Qornoloosa keeththe gelin Qornoloossi iza mokki ekkidi iza toho bolla hokki goynnides.
\v 26 Gido attin Phexroosi “Takka ne mala asakko! Denda” giidi denthides.
\p 
\v 27 Phexroosikka iza haasayssishe izara so gelishin daro derey shiiqi uttidayssa beyides.
\v 28 Izikka istas “Ayhuda asi hara dere asara gaaggonta mala woykko hara dere as gididayta mata shiiqonta mala nu wogay diggizayssa inte ereeta. Gido attin ta oonakka tuna woykko izi geesh deenna goonta mala Xoossi taas qoncisides.
\v 29 Hessa gish ta xeeygetida wode hekko sidhonta yadis. Histin inte tana aazas xeygidakkone erana koyays” gides.
\p 
\v 30 Qornoloosikka “Oyddu gallassafe kase likke hanni wode gallassafe uddufun saaten tani ta soon woossishin qopponta booththa may7o may7ida asi yiidi ta sinthan eqqidi
\v 31 tana ‘Qornoloosa! Ne woossay siyetides; ne manqotas immiza muxuwatay Xoossa sinthi gakkides.
\v 32 Hessa gish Iyophphe katama as kiittada Phexroosa geetettiza Simoona ehissa. Izi abba achchan galba qaaciza Simoona keeththan imathateth dees’ gides.
\v 33 Takka heerakka neekko as kiittadis. Ne yuussaykka lo7o. Histikko Goday nena azazidayssa ne nuus yootikko Xoossi yootidayssa neeppe siyanas nu wurikka hayssan Xoossa sinthan doos” gides.
\p 
\v 34 Phexroosikka “Xoossi oonaka shaakki maadontayssa ta tumappe eradis. \x * \xo 10:34 \xt Zaare 10:17\x*
\v 35 Gido attin Xoossas babbizaytanne xillo ooththizayta wursi oona baggafe gidinka izi ekkees.
\v 36 Xoossi ubbas Goda gidida Yesus Kirstoosa baggara Isra7eele asas kiittida sarotetha Mishiraachcho kiitay hayssa.
\v 37 Yohannisi xinqata gish sabakidappe guyen Galilappe doommidi kumeththa Yuhudan hanidayssa inte ereeta.
\v 38 Xoossi Naazirete Yesusa Xillo Ayananinne wolqan tiyides. Izikka Xoossi izara diza gish ba gakkidason ubban lo7o ooththishe Xala7e godateththa giddon dizayta wursi pathides.
\p 
\v 39 “Izi Ayhudata dereninne Yerusalame kataman ooththidayssa ubbas nu marka. Qasseka asay iza mitha bolla kaqqi wodhides.
\v 40 Gido attin Xoossi iza heedzdzantho gallas heyqoppe denthidessinne asi iza beyana mala ooththides.
\v 41 Izi qonciday asa ubbas gidonta hayqoppe dendin izara midaytassinne izara uyidaytas Xoossi koyro doorida nuus iza markatassa.
\v 42 Izi nu derezas sabakana malanne hayqqidayta bollanne paxa dizayta bolla pirdanas Xoossi shuumiday iza gididayssa nu markattana mala nuna azazides.
\v 43 Iza ammanidadey wuri iza sunthan nagara maaretidi geeyanayssa nabeti izas markatettes” gi yooto doommides.
\p 
\v 44 Phexroosi hessa haasayishin qaala siyizayta ubba bolla Xillo Ayanay wodhdhides.
\v 45 Qaxxaretidayta baggafe Phexroosara yida ammanizayti Xillo Ayana imotethi Ayzaabeta bolla wodhdhishin beyidi malaletida.
\v 46 Hessika isti dumma qaalan haasayishininne Xoossa galatishin siyida gishassa. He wode Phexroosi,
\p 
\v 47 “Hayti asati nu mala Xillo Ayana ekkida gish isti haaththan xammaqetonta mala ista digganay oonnee?” gides.
\v 48 Hessa gish Yesus Kirstoosa sunthan xammaqettana mala azazides. Hessafe guye Phexroosi guuththa wode istara daana mala woossida.
\c 11
\s1 Phexroosi Ayzaabeta keeththe ayssi gelidakkone walassida
\p 
\v 1 Hawaaretinne Yuhudan diza ammanizayti Ayzaabeti Xoossa qaala ekkidayssa siyida.
\v 2 Hessa gish Phexroosi pude Yerusalame kezin qaxxaretida Ayhudappe ammanizayti Phexroosa,
\v 3 “Ne qaxxaretonta asata keeth gelada istara kath madasa” giidi walassida.
\p 
\v 4 Phexroosi qasse istas gelana mala maarara hizgi yootides.
\v 5 “Tani Iyophphe kataman woossishin dhisikko mala tana liphiphi histidi ajjutan gita may7o misatiza miishi oyddu baggara oyketidi saloppe ta dizaso wodhdhishin beyadis.
\v 6 Ta tishshi hista xeellishin oyddu tohora diza meheta, wora do7ata, biitta bolla gooshettiza medhetethatanne salo bolla piradhiza kafota beyadis.
\v 7 Heerakka tana ‘Phexroosa denda! Hayssa shukada ma’ giza qaala siyadis.
\p 
\v 8 “Takka ‘Godo hessi hanenna; tani tuna woykko geesh gidontayssa mulekka ta duunakko shiisha erikke’ gadis.
\p 
\v 9 “He kase qaalay qasseka ‘Xoossi geeshidayssa ne tunisoppa’ giidi saloppe taas yootides.
\v 10 Hessika heedzdzuto shireti shireti yootetidappe guye wurikka simmidi pude salo bides.
\p 
\v 11 “Qisaariyappe taakko kiitettida heedzdzu asati heerakka he saateyn yi gakkidi ta diza keeththa karen eqqida.
\v 12 Ta aynne sidhonta istara baana mala Xillo Ayanay taas yootides. He usuppun ishati tanara issife biidi addeza keeththe geldos.
\v 13 Izikka Xoossa kiitanchay iza keeththan eqqidi izas beettidayssanne ‘Iyophphe geetettizaso as yeddada Phexroosa geetettiza Simoona xeygisa.
\v 14 Izi yiidi nenanne neso asa wursi ashshana qaala yootana’ gidayssa nuus yootides.
\p 
\v 15 “Takka baada buro yooto oykkishin koyro Xillo Ayanay kase nu bolla wodhdhoyssatho ista bollaka wodhdhides.
\v 16 Kase Goday nuus yootishe ‘Yohannisi haaththan xammaqides shin inte Xillo Ayanan xammaqettana’ gida qaalay heerakka taas qofetides. \x * \xo 11:16 \xt Hawa 1:5\x*
\v 17 Hessa gish nuni Goda Yesus Kirstoosa ammanishin nuus immida Xillo Ayana Xoossi istas immikko histin Xoossara eqqetanas tani oonee?” gides.
\p 
\v 18 Isti hessa siyida wode istas gizazi dhayin co7u gi simmidi “Hayssa mala gidikko Ayzaabetikka ha ooratha de7okko yaana mala Xoossi asas maaroteth immides guussa” giidi Xoossa galatida.
\s1 Anxokiyan diza Woosa Keeththayo
\p 
\v 19 Istifanoose bolla dendida goodeteththa gaason laalettida ammaniza asay qaala Ayhudatas xalala yootishe Pinqe, Qophiroosenne Anxokiya geetettizaso gakkanaas kanthi bida. \x * \xo 11:19 \xt Hawa 8:1-4\x*
\v 20 Qophirooseppenne Qareenappe yida issi issi asati Anxokiya biidi Giriketasikka Goda Yesusa Mishiraachcho qaala yootida.
\v 21 Goda maadoykka istara dees; Qoodan keehi daro asay ammanidi Godakko simmides.
\p 
\v 22 Hessa woreykka Yerusalamen diza Woosa Keeththa asa haythan wodhdhin Woosa Keeththaya Barnabaasa Anxokiya yeddadus.
\v 23 Izikka he bi gakkidi Xoossi ba aadho kiyateth deraas immidayssa beyidi ufayetidessinne asay wurikka kumeththa woznappe Goda ammanon minnana mala zorides.
\v 24 Izikka Xillo Ayananinne ammanon kumida lo7o asa. Daro derey Goda ammanon gujettides.
\p 
\v 25 Hessafe kaallidi Barnabaassi Sawule koyana Xarseese bides.
\v 26 Iza demmidi Anxokiya ekki yides. Nam7aykka heen diza Woosa Keeththa asara gididi layth kumeth daro dere tamarsida. Heen Anxokiyan ammanizayti koyro “Kirsaane” geetetti xeeygetida.
\p 
\v 27 He wode issi issi nabeti Yerusalameppe duge Anxokiya wodhdhida.
\v 28 Ista giddofe issoy Agaboossa geetettizayssi dendi eqqidi Xillo Ayanay iza bessin alame ubban gita koshay dendanayssa yootides. Hessika Oroome kawo Qalawodosa Qeesare geetettizayssa kawoteththa wode poletides. \x * \xo 11:28 \xt Hawa 21:10\x*
\v 29 Ammanizayti wuri issoy issoy ba wolqa keena miishe kesettidi Yuhudan diza ammaniza ishata maaddanas qachida.
\v 30 Maado miisha kesettidi Barnabaasanne Sawule kushen cimatas gaththana mala yeddida.
\c 12
\s1 Ammanizayta bolla gakkida gita metonne goodeteth
\p 
\v 1 He wode kawo Herdoossi issi issi ammaniza asa gooddi gooddi metothides.
\v 2 Yohannisa isha Yaqoobe mashshan wodhisides.
\v 3 Izikka hessa ooththiday Ayhudata ufaysidayssa beyidi Phexroosakka oythides. Hessika haniday Ayhudatas uketha ba7aale geetettiza ba7aale gallassa.
\v 4 Phexroosakka qasho keeththe gelsidappe guye oyddu oyddu wotadarati taran taran naagana mala giigettida wotadaratas immides. Izi hessatho ooththiday Paaziga ba7aaley aadhdhida mala kessidi derey pirdana mala shiishanaasa. \x * \xo 12:4 \xt Kessa 12:1-27\x*
\v 5 Hessa gish Phexroosa qasho keeththe gelsidi naagetes. Gido attin Woosa Keeththa asay izas keehi mino woossa woossides.
\p 
\v 6 Herdoossi Phexroosa dereza sinth shiishana qoppi utti dishin he qamma gidoth nam7u sansalatan qashetidi nam7u wotadarata giddon ichchides. Qasho keeththa naagizayti keeththa penge bolla eqqi naagishin,
\v 7 Goda kiitanchay ezigonta istas beettides. Isti diza kifilen poo7oy poo7ides. Kiitanchazikka Phexroosa mille bochchi beeggoththidi “Elle denda!” gides. Heerakka sansalatay iza kusheppe gaden wodhdhides.
\p 
\v 8 Kiitanchazi iza “Ne may7o may7a! Caammakka aaththa!” giin Phexroosikka azazettida mala ooththides; qasseka kiitanchay “Ne gaabe may7ada tana kaalla” gides.
\v 9 Phexroosikka qasho keeththafe iza kaalli kezides. Gido attin izas agumo beyiza misatides attin kiitanchazi ooththizayssi tumu gididayssa eribenna.
\v 10 Koyro zabetappenne nam7antho zabetappe aadhdhidi gede katama kessiza oge bolla diza birata pengako gakkida. Pengeykka barka doyetti wodhdhides. Isti kezi bida. Isti qeeri oge dizaaro aadhdhida mala kiitanchazi izappe shaaketides.
\p 
\v 11 Phexroosas kahay simmishin “Goday ba kiitancha kiittidi iza Herdoosa kusheppenne Ayhudati ta bolla qoppida ubbafe tana kessidayssa ta ha7i tumappe eradis” gides.
\p 
\v 12 Hessa akeekki eridappe guye daro asay issi bolla shiiqetidi woossiza Marqoosa geetettiza Yohannisa aayo Maaramiso bides.
\v 13 Izi he biidi kare penge qooxin issi Roodo geetettiza garadeya kare ooni qoxxizakkonne eranas kare mata badus.
\v 14 Qaalay Phexroosayssa gididayssa erada keeha ufayetida gish kare doyonta wothan guye simmada “Phexroosi Karen penge bolla eqqides” gadus.
\p 
\v 15 Asaykka izo “Hanne gooyay!” gida. Iza qas zaara zaara istas yootin “Histikko hessi iza naagiza kiitancha gidonta aggenna” gida.
\p 
\v 16 Phexroosi qas penge qoth gujjides. Istika penga doydi iza beyida mala malalettida.
\v 17 Izikka isti co7u gaana mala ba kushen malati bessidi Goday iza qashosoppe wosti kessidakkonne lo7ethi yootides. “Hayssa wursi Yaqoobesinne hanko ammanizaytas yootite” gides. Hessafekka gede haraso bides.
\p 
\v 18 Wontetha gallas wontara wotadarati “Phexroosi waanidee?” gishe ba giddon bul7akettida.
\v 19 Herdoossi Phexroosa as yeddi koysidi izi dhayida gish naagizayta lo7ethi oychidappe guye ista wodhana mala azazides. Hessafe guye Herdoossi Yuhudappe duge Qisaariya wodhdhidi heen uttides.
\s1 Herdoosa hayqo
\p 
\v 20 Herdoosikka Xiroose asaranne Sidoona asara oosha. He dere asay kath demmizay Herodossa dereppe gidida gish he dere kawo xeellizade Bilasxoosappe maado qaala demmida mala issi bolla gididi Herdoosara maqaynthanas oychida.
\p 
\v 21 Giigana barettida gallas Herdoossi kawoteththa may7o may7idi kawoteththa algan uttidi deraas haasayides.
\v 22 Derezikka “Hayssi Xoossa qaalappe attin asa qaala deenna!” gi waassides.
\v 23 Herdoosikka Xoossas boncho immoonta aggida gish Goda kiitanchay heerakka Herdoosa shoci yeggin guxuni hayqqides.
\p 
\v 24 Xoossa qaalay gidikko diccidi akki akki bides.
\v 25 Barnabaassinne Sawuley ba ekki bida kiita polidi Yerusalame simmidi Marqoosa geetettiza Yohannisaka banara ekki simmida.
\c 13
\s1 Barnabaassinne Sawuley kiitettida
\p 
\v 1 Anxokiyan diza Woosa Keeththan nabetinne astamareti deettes. Heytikka Barnabaassinne Negeere geetettiza Simoonara, Qareena dere as Luqiyoosara, Herdoosara issife dicida Minaheranne Sawulera wuri issife deettes. \f + \fr 13:1 \ft Negerey Laatine qaala gidishin birsheththay kareth guussa.\f*
\v 2 Heyti wuri Godas goynnishenne xoomishe dishin Xillo Ayanay “Barnabaasanne Sawule ta ista xeygida oosos taas shaakki kessite” gides.
\v 3 Istika xoomi woossidi ba kushe ista bolla woththidappe guye moyzida.
\s1 Barnabassinne Sawuley Qophiroose geetettizason
\p 
\v 4 Barnabassinne Sawuley Xillo Ayana kiitan duge Selawuqiya wodhdhida; heeppeka markaben geellidi Qophiroose bida.
\v 5 Salmeena geetettizaso gakkidi Ayhudata Woosa Keeththatan Xoossa qaala sabakida; Marqoosa geetettiza Yohannisikka istara biidi ista maaddides.
\p 
\v 6 Abba giddon diza biitta Qophiroose geetettiza dereyo ha gaxappe he gaxa gakkanaas kanthi kezidi Phaafa geetettizaso gakkishin issi Ayhuda asa shin maronne wordo nabe Bar-Yesusa geetettiza as demmida.
\v 7 Izikka issi Sargoosa Phawuloosa geetettiza woznama dere ayssizayssara issife dees. Ha dere ayssiza addezi Xoossa qaala siyana koydi Barnabaasanne Sawule xeygisides.
\v 8 Marozi Ellimaassi ba suntha birsheththa mala dere ayssizayssi ammanonta mala dhuphanas koydi istara eqqetides.
\v 9 Phawuloosa geetettida Sawuley Xillo Ayanay izan kumin maroza tishshi histi xeelidi,
\v 10 “Neno xillotetha ubbas morkezo! Geneynne iitatethi nenan kumidaysso haysso dabuloosa nawu! Goda suure oge geellaseththafe shempikii?
\v 11 Hekko ha7i Goda kushey ne bolla dees. Ne qooqana; hannife guye awa arshe poo7o Issinokka beyakka” gides.
\p Heerakka shaarumaynne dhumay iza bolla wodhdhides. Kushe oykki bana kaalethanade koshshi yaanne haanne gides.
\v 12 Dere ayssizayssi ha hanida yo7oza beyidi goda gish siyida timirten malaletidi ammanides.
\s1 Barnabassinne Sawuley Phissidiya geetettiza deren
\p 
\v 13 Phawuloosinne izara dizayti Phaafappe dendidi Phinfiliya geetettizason diza Phergene geetettizaso markaben geli bida; Yohannisi istafe shaaketidi guye Yerusalame simmides.
\v 14 Isti gidikko Phergeneppe dendidi Phissidiya giddon diza gede Anxokiya bida; Sambata gallas Ayhudata woossa keeth geli uttida.
\v 15 Muse woga maxaafatinne nabeta maxaafati nababetidappe guye Ayhudata Woosa Keeththa halaqati “Nu ishato! Intes hayssa asa zorana qaalay diikko haasayte” giidi istako ase yeddida.
\p 
\v 16 Phawuloosika dendi eqqidi ba kushera malatidi “Inteno Isra7eele asato! Qasseka inteno Xoossas yayyiza Ayzaabeto! siyite.
\v 17 Ha Isra7eele dere Xoossay kase nu aawata doorides; isti Gibxe deren dishin ista dhoqu dhoqu histides. Ba wolqama qesera heeppe ista kessides. \x * \xo 13:17 \xt Kessa 1:7; 12:51\x*
\v 18 Oyddu tammu layth kumeth ista bazzo biittan dandayides. \f + \fr 13:18 \fq dandayides \ft issi issi Geeshsha Maxaafati ista lo7ethi oykkides geetes.\f*\x * \xo 13:18 \xt Tay 14:34; Zaare 1:31\x*
\v 19 Kanaane biittan dizayta laapun kawota dhayssidi ista biitta ba deretas gade histi laattissides. \x * \xo 13:19 \xt Zaare 7:1; Iya 14:1\x*
\v 20 Hessi wuri poletiday oyddu xeetanne ichashu tammu laythata giddonna. Hessafe guye nabe Sameela wode gakkanaas ista pirdiza daannata immides. \x * \xo 13:20 \xt Dane 2:16; 1Same 3:20\x*
\p 
\v 21 “Hessafe guye derey ba bolla kawo kawoththana mala Sameela woossides; Xoossayka Biniyaame baggafe Qiise naa Sa7oole istas immides. Izikka ista oyddu tammu layth haarides. \x * \xo 13:21 \xt 1Same 8:5; 10:21\x*
\v 22 Sa7oole shaaridappe guye Dawute kawothides; iza gish ‘Ta wozna mala hanizayssanne ta koyidayssa wursi ooththiza Iseeye naa Dawute ta demmadis’ giidi Dawute gish Xoossi markattides. \x * \xo 13:22 \xt 1Same 13:14; 16:12; Maza 89:20\x*
\v 23 Xoossika ba caaqo qaalatho ha addeza zerethafe as ashshizayssa Yesusa Isra7eeles ehides.
\v 24 Yesusi yaanappe kase Yohannisi Isra7eele derey wuri maarotethan gelidi xammaqettana mala sabakides. \x * \xo 13:24 \xt Mar 1:4; Luqa 3:3\x*
\v 25 Yohannisi ba kiitettidayssa polo bolla dishe ‘Ta intes oona misatazinaa? Ta kiitettidayssa gidikke haray attoshin ta izas toho caamma kire birshanas bessontayssi taappe guyera yaana’ gides. \x * \xo 13:25 \xt Yoha 1:20; Mato 3:11; Mar 1:7; Luqa 3:16; Yoha 1:27\x*
\p 
\v 26 “Inteno Abrahaame zerethafe yeletida nu ishato! Qasseka inte giddonka Xoossas yayyizayti wuri hayssi atotetha kiitay kiitettiday nuus ubbatassa!
\v 27 Yerusalame asatinne ista halaqati Yesusa eribetenna; gido attin isti iza bolla pirdida; hessanka sambatan sambatan nababetiza kase nabeta qaalay iza bolla polettides.
\v 28 Iza hayqos gaththiza issi gaasokka isti demmoonta aggikkokka Philaxoosi iza bolla hayqo pirda pirdana mala woossida. \x * \xo 13:28 \xt Mato 27:22-23; Mar 15:13-14; Luqa 23:21-23; Yoha 19:15\x*
\v 29 Iza gish xaafetidayssa isti wursi polidappe guye iza kaqqettida mitha bollafe gaden woththidi duufon moogida. \x * \xo 13:29 \xt Mato 27:57-61; Mar 15:42-47; Luqa 23:50-56; Yoha 19:38-42\x*
\v 30 Gido attin Xoossi iza hayqoppe denthides.
\v 31 Galilappe Yerusalame gakkanaas banara dizaytas daro wode beettides; heytikka ha7i iza gish deretas markata. \x * \xo 13:31 \xt Hawa 1:3\x*
\p 
\v 32 “Nukka kase Xoossi nu Aawatas caaqida Mishiraachcho qaala intes sabakoos.
\v 33 Yesusa kiittidi istas caaqida qaala nuus ista naytas polides; hessika mazamure maxaafan nam7antho shempon ‘Ne ta naaza; ta nena hach yeladis’ geetetti xaafetides. \x * \xo 13:33 \xt Maza 2:7\x*
\v 34 Qasseka izi wooqontayssanne Xoossi iza hayqoppe denthidayssa shaakki erana mala
\q2 ‘Anjettidayssanne ammanettida
\q3 Dawute anjo ta intes immana’ gides. \x * \xo 13:34 \xt Isa 55:3\x*
\q1 
\v 35 Hessa gish harasonka
\q3 ‘Ne geeshshay hayqqi wooqana mala ne koyakka’ gees. \x * \xo 13:35 \xt Maza 16:10\x*
\p 
\v 36 “Dawutey ba woden Xoossa shene mala ooththidappe guye hayqides; kase ba aawatara moogetin iza ashoy wooqides.
\v 37 Xoossi iza hayqoppe denthidayssi izi gidikko wooqibenna.
\v 38 Hessa gish ta ishato! Nagaras maarotethi beettizay Yesusa baggara gididayssi intes sabaketidayssa erite.
\v 39 Iza ammanizadey wuri kase Muse woga baggara demmoonta xilloteth demmana.
\v 40-41 Hessa gish kase nabeti
\q2 ‘Inteno qidhizayto xeellite, malaletitenne, dhayite,
\q3 intes oonikka yootin ammananas intena metiza miish
\q3 ta inte woden ooththana’ gida qaalay inte bolla gakkonta mala naagetite” gides.
\p 
\v 42 Phawuloosinne Barnabaassi Ayhudata Woosa Keeththafe kezishin asay ista hessa isti yootida qaala kaalliza Sambata gallas zaari yootana mala woossides.
\v 43 Shiiqoy laalettidappe guye daro Ayhudatinne Ayhudata ammanon gelidi Xoosse goynniza asati Phawuloosanne Barnabaasa kaallida. Phawuloosantika ista qofsishe isti Xoossa kiyatethan minni daana mala zorida.
\p 
\v 44 Kaalliza Sambata gallas katama asappe guuththati xalala attin dariza baggay wuri Goda qaala siyana shiiqides.
\v 45 Ayhudatikka daro dere beyidi qanatetethan kumida. Phawuloosa haasaya eqqetishe iza cayida.
\p 
\v 46-47 Phawuloosinne Barnabaassi babbonta xalateththan “Xoossa qaalay koyro intes yootetanas bessees. Gido attin inte qaala leqqideta. Intes merna de7oy bessontayssa interka inte bolla pirdida gish ha7i nuni gede Ayzaabetakko baana koyoos. Qasseka Goday nuna ‘Asas atotetha qaala biitta gaxa gaththana mala ta nena Ayzaabetas poo7o hista kiittadis’ gi azazides” gida.
\p 
\v 48 Ayzaabeti hessa siydi daro ufayetida. Goda qaalasikka boncho immida. Merna de7os giigettida derey wuri ammanides.
\v 49 Goda qaalay heeran diza dere ubbaso gakkides.
\v 50 Ayhudati qas Ayana hanon kaseppe minnizaytanne duussan bonchettida macasata hessathoka kataman diza gita asata dentheththidi Phawuloosa bollanne Barnabaasa bolla goodeteththi denthidi ba dereppe kessi gooddida.
\v 51 Phawuloosinne Barnabaasi asay ista ixidayssa bessanas ba toho bolla diza gudulla pittidi Iqoniyoone geetettizaso bida. \x * \xo 13:51 \xt Mato 10:14; Mar 6:11; Luqa 9:5; 10:11\x*
\v 52 Ammaniizayti ufayssaninne Xillo Ayanan kumida.
\c 14
\s1 Phawuloosinne Barnabaassi Iqoniyoonen
\p 
\v 1 Iqoniyoonen Phawuloosinne Barnabaassi issife Ayhudata Woosa Keeththe gelida. Henka isti asa lo7eth tamarsida gish Girike asappenne Ayhuda asappe daroy ammanides.
\v 2 Hinko ammanonta Ayhuda asay Ayzaabeta ista bolla dentheththidi asay ammanizayta ixana mala ooththides.
\v 3 Phawuloosinne barnabaassi Goda gish xalatethara asas yootishe heen daro wode gam7ida. Godayka isti yootiza iza qaala gita malataranne wolqama ooson qoncisi markattides.
\v 4 Katama asay ba giddon nam7u kezi shaaketidi baggay Ayhudata bagga baggay Phawuloosanta bagga gidides.
\p 
\v 5 He wode Ayhudatinne Ayzaabeti bana kaaleththizaytara issife gididi ista waayssanassinne shuchchan caddanas koyda.
\v 6 Istika hessa erida mala Listiranne Derbeene geetettizaso gede Liqa7ooniya katamatanne he heeran diza dere baqatida.
\v 7 Henka mishiraachcho qaala sabako doommida.
\s1 Phawuloosinne Barnabaasi Listiraninne Derbeenen
\p 
\v 8 Listiran yeeletosappe ba tohora hamuti eronta issi toho sila addey dees.
\v 9-10 Hessadey Phawuloosi sabakishin utti siyees; Phawuloosikka izakko tishshi histi xeelidi addeza pathana ammanoy iza bolla dizayssa beyidinne qaala dhoqu histidi “Sitti gaada ne tohon eqqa!” gides. Addezi heerakka guppi dendidi hamuth oykkides.
\p 
\v 11 Asay Phawuloosi ooththidayssa beyidi Liqa7ooniya qaalara “Eeqa Xoossati as misatidi ha nuukko wodhdhida” giidi waassides.
\v 12 Barnabaasa “Diya” gida Phawuloosakka haasayiza waannay iza gidida gish “Hermeene” gida.
\v 13 Katamappe asi bayndason diza Diya geetettiza eeqa keeththa Qeesey kormatanne xaaxeti giigida ciish gede katama geliza oge bolla efidi derezara issife gididi Phawuloosasinne Barnabaasas yarshana koyides.
\p 
\v 14 Hawaareti Barnabaassinne Phawuloosi hessa siyida mala ba may7o daakkidi gede dereza giddo woxxida; ba qaala dhoqu histidi hizgida;
\v 15 “Hayto asato! Hayssa aazas ooththetii? Nukka inte mala assako! Inteka qasse hayssa mela hada yo7oppe haakkidi salonne sa7a, abbaka, abbata giddon dizayta wursi medhdhida de7o Xoossakko inte simmana mala intes mishiraachcho qaala sabakoos. \x * \xo 14:15 \xt Kessa 20:11; Maza 146:6\x*
\v 16 Izi kase aadhdhida yeletethaynne derey wurikka ba koyda mala hananas yeddi bessides.
\v 17 Gido attin Xoossi saloppe iranne hessaththokka kaththi kaxxiza wodeta immidi inte wozna kaththaninne ufayssa kunthides; ufayssaka intena kalthidi lo7o ooson bana markay baynda aggibenna” gida.
\v 18 Hessa wursi haasayidi asay istas yarshonta mala waaydi diggida.
\p 
\v 19 Ayhudati qas Anxokiyappenne Iqoniyooneppe yida asay asa zoridi Phawuloosa shuchchan caddana mala ammanthida. Phawuloosakka shuchchan caddidinne hayqqides gi goochchidi katamappe gede kare kessida.
\v 20 Gido attin ammanizayti iza yuuyi aadhdhi naagishin Phawuloosi dendidi gede katama gelides. Wontetha gallas Barnabaasara issife Derbeene geetettizaso bida.
\s1 Phawuloosinne Barnabaassi Sooriyan diza Anxokiya simmida
\p 
\v 21 Phawuloosinne Barnabaasi Darbeen mishiraachcho qaala sabakida daro asa ammanthidappe guye gede Listira, Iqoniyoonenne Anxokiya simmida.
\v 22 Ammanzayta wozna minthethishe isti ammanon minni daana mala zorishe “Nu Xoossa kawoteth gelanas daro meto giddora aadhdhanaas koshshees” gida.
\v 23 Hessafe guye dumma dumma Woosa Keeththatan cimata dooridappe guye xoomaninne woossan ammanettida Godas hadara aaththi immida.
\p 
\v 24 Phissidiyara aadhdhidi Phinfiliya simmida.
\v 25 Phergenen qaala sabakidi duge Axaaliya geetettizaso wodhdhida.
\v 26 Axaaliyappekka ha7i gakkanaas isti ooththida oosoza hadara istas imettida katama Sooriyan diza Anxokiya markaben gelidi simmida.
\p 
\v 27 He gakkida mala Woosa Keeththa asa wursi shiishshidi Xoossi istara ooththidayssa qasseka Ayzaabetas ammano pengey waani doyettidakkonne wursi yootida.
\v 28 Heen ammanizaytara daro wode gam7ida.
\c 15
\s1 Yerusalame duulata
\p 
\v 1 Issi issi asati Yuhudappe duge Anxokiya wodhdhidi “Inte Muse woga mala qaxxaretonta aggikko oonikka attanas dandayekketa” giidi ammanizayta tamarso doommida. \x * \xo 15:1 \xt Lewe 12:3\x*
\v 2 Hessika Phawuloosanne Barnabaasa gita palamaninne oosha giddo gelthides; hessa gish Phawuloosinne Barnabaassi hara issi issi ammaniza asatara Yerusalame kezidi ha yo7oza gish cimatanne Hawaareta oychana mala geetettides.
\p 
\v 3 Hessa gish Woosa Keeththaya ista Yerusalame baana mala kiittin isti Pinqeranne Samaariyara aadhdhi bishe heen diza asa Ayzaabeti ammanon simmidayssa yootida; he wode ammanizayti hessa siydi keehi ufayettida.
\v 4 Isti Yerusalame gakkin Woosa Keeththa asay Hawaaretinne cimati ista mokki ekkida; kiitetti bidaytikka Xoossi istara gididi ooththidayssa wursi istas yootida.
\v 5 Farsaaweeta bagga asatappe ammanida issi issi asati dendidi “Ayzaabeti qaxxaretanassinne Muse woga naagana mala istas yootanas bessees” gida.
\p 
\v 6 Hawaaretinne cimati he yo7oza giddo lo7eth xeellanas shiiqida.
\v 7 Daro palamappe guye Phexroosi dendi eqqidi, “Ta ishato! Guuththa wodeppe kase Xoossi tana inte giddofe dooridi Ayzaabeti ta duunappe mishiraachcho qaala siydi ammanana mala ooththidayssa inte ereeta.
\v 8 Asa wozna eriza Xoossi nuus immidayssa mala istaska Xillo Ayana immidi ista baas ekkidayssa markatides. \x * \xo 15:8 \xt Hawa 10:44\x*
\v 9 Ista woznakka ammanon geeshshidi nu giddoninne ista giddon aykko shaakkokka ooththibenna.
\v 10 Hessa gish nu aawatinne nukka tookkanaas dandayonta qambara ammanizayta toossanas inte aazas Xoosse paacetii?
\v 11 Nu attiday likke istaththokka Goda Yesusa aadho kiyatethan gididayssa ammanoos” gides.
\p 
\v 12 Shiiqida asay wurikka co7u giin Barnabaassinne Phawuloosi Xoossi ista baggara Ayzaabeta giddon ooththida gita malatata gish yootishin malaletidi lo7ethi siyides.
\v 13 Isti yooti wursishin Yaqoobey dendi eqqidi hizgides “Ta ishato! Ta gizayssa siyite;
\v 14 Xoossi Ayzaabetappe baas gidana dere kasetidi izi wosti xeygi woththidako Simooni nuus lo7ethi yootides.
\v 15 Kase nabetan hizgi xaafetida qaalay hayssara gaggees.
\q1 
\v 16 ‘Hayssafe guye ta simmada
\q3 laaletida Dawute keeththe keexana;
\q3 laalettidayssa zaara essana; zaaradakka keexana.
\q1 
\v 17 Hessika attida asay Goda koyana malanne
\q3 ta sunthan xeeygettida Ayzaabeti tana koyana
\q3 mala gees wursi ooththida Xoossi;
\v 18 Hayssa koyroppekka ersida Xoossi tana’ gides.
\p 
\v 19 “Hessa gish ha Xoossako simmida Ayzaabeta nu metothonta mala hayssi ta baggara taas qasho.
\v 20 Gido attin eeqas yarshettidi tunida kath mooppite; laymappe haakkite; bawuti hayqqida mehe asho mooppite; suuth uyoppite giidi nu istas xaafana bessees. \x * \xo 15:20 \xt Kessa 34:15-17; Lewe 18:6-23\x*
\v 21 Muse wogay gidikko benisofe Sambata Sambata gallas Ayhudata Woosa Keeththan nabebetishenne katamay dizason sabaketishe dees” gides.
\s1 Hawaaretappe ammaniza Ayzaabetas xaafettida dabdaabe
\p 
\v 22 He wode Hawaaretinne cimati kumeththa Woosa Keeththa asara gididi ba giddofe issi issi asata dooridi Phawuloosaranne Barnabaasara gaththi Anxokiya yeddanas qachida. Ammaniza asa giddofe waannatizayta Barsabaasa geetettiza Yuhudanne Sillase doorida.
\v 23 Ista kushen immi yeddida dabdaabezi “Inte ishatappe, Hawaaretappe, cimatappe, Ayzaabetappe ammanida Anxokiyaninne Sooriyan, Kilqiyanka diza ammanizaytas nu sarokay intena gakko.
\p 
\v 24 “Issi issi asati nuuppe gidonta ba baggara nu achchafe biidi ba haasayan inte wozna yaanne haanne qaathidayssanne intena bul7akkidayssa nu siyidos.
\v 25 Hessa gish guutha asata dooridi dosettida Barnabaasaranne Phawuloosara inteko yeddanas nu wurikka qaala gaaggidos.
\v 26 Isti Goda Yesus Kirstoosa gish ba shempo aaththi immidayta.
\v 27 Hessa gish nu intes xaafidayssa isti intes ba duunara lo7ethi yootana mala Yuhudanne Sillase inteko yeddidos.
\v 28 Hayta intes koshshiza yo7otappe hara deexo tooho nu inte bolla wothonta mala nussinne Xillo Ayanas lo7o misati beettides.
\v 29 Hessika inte eeqas shukettida ashoppe, suuthafe, bawuti hayqqida mehe ashoppenne laymappe inte hakkana mala; inte hayta misatizaytappe haakkikko intes lo7o; saron diite” gees.
\p 
\v 30 Kiitettida asati moyzetidi duge Anxokiya wodhdhida; heen ammanizayta wursi shiishshidi ehida dabdaabeza istas immida.
\v 31 Dereyka nababidi minthethiza qaalan ufayetides.
\v 32 Yuhudaynne Sillassi nabeta gidida gish daro zoridi ammanizayta minthethida.
\v 33 Heen guutha wode gam7idi ammaniza asay moyzin guye bana kiittidaytakko simmida.
\v 34 Sillassi qas heen attanas koyides. \f + \fr 15:34 \ft Issi issi Geeshsha Maxaafati paydo 34 bolla diza qofa gujjettenna.\f*
\v 35 Phawuloosinne Barnabaassi hara daro asatara gididi Goda qaala tamarsishenne sabakishe Anxokiyan gam7ida.
\s1 Phawuloosanne Barnabaasa shaaketeth
\p 
\v 36 Phawuloosi guutha wode gam7idi Barnabaasa “Nu kase Goda qaala yootida ubba katamata biidi ammanzayti ay mala dizaakkonne ane yuuyi beyoos, denda” gides.
\v 37 Barnabaasikka Marqoosa geetettiza Yohannisi istara baana mala koyides.
\v 38 Phawuloosi qas iza ekki baanas koybenna; gaasoyka kase Marqoossi istafe shaaketidi Phinfiliya gizason guye attidi istara oosos sinth kezonta aggida gishassa. \x * \xo 15:38 \xt Hawa 13:13\x*
\v 39 Histin daro palamay ista giddon medhetida gish ba giddon shaaketi wodhdhida; hessa gish Barnabaassi Marqoosa ekkidi markaben gelidi Qophiroose bides.
\v 40 Phawuloosi qas Sillase doorides. Ammanzaytikka Phawuloosa Goda aadho kiyatethas hadara immidappe guye izi istafe shaaketidi bides.
\v 41 Ammanizayta minthethishe Sooriyaranne Kilqiyara aadhdhi bides.
\c 16
\s1 Ximtoossi Phawuloosaranne Sillasera issife gidides
\p 
\v 1 Phawuloosi Derbeene geetettizasone Listira gakkidi iza aaway Girike as, aayiya qas Ayhuda as gidida Ximtoosa geetettiza issi ammanizade heen demmides.
\v 2 Izikka Listiraninne Iqoniyoon ammaniza asa achchan lo7o markateth dizadde.
\v 3 Phawuloosikka Ximtoosa banara ekki baanas koyides. Hessa gish he heeran Ayhudata gish giidi Ximtoosa qaxxarides. Gaasoyka Ayhudati Ximtoosa aaway Girike as gididayssa eriza gishassa.
\p 
\v 4 Isti issi katamappe hara katama aadhdhi aadhdhi bishe Hawaaretinne Yerusalame Woosa Keeththa cimati yeddida kiita asay ekkidi naagana mala ammaniza asas immi immi aadhdhida.
\v 5 Woosa keeththa asay ammanon minni minni bides; qasse asaykka qoodan gallas gallas gujetti gujetti bides.
\s1 Phawuloosi Maqidooniya gish beyida ajjuta
\p 
\v 6 Phawuloosinne izara diza zatati qaala Iisiyan sabakonta mala Xillo Ayanay diggida gish Pirgiyaranne Galatiya derera aadhdhi bida.
\v 7 Isti Miisiya geetettizaso gakkana matishe Bitiniya geetettizaso gelana qoppin Yesusa Ayanay ista diggides.
\v 8 Hessa gish Miisiyara aadhdhidi Xiro7aada geetettizaso wodhdhida.
\v 9 Issi Maqidooniya asi eqqidi Phawuloosa ha Maqidooniya pinnada nuna maadda gishin Phawuloosi omars ajjutan beyides.
\v 10 Izikka he ajjuta beyidi Xoossi nu istas Mishiraachcho qaala yootana mala xeygides gi qachidi nu heerakka gede Maqidooniya baana koyidos.
\s1 Piliphoosen Liidiyay Goda ammanadus
\p 
\v 11 Markabera Xiro7aada geetettizasoppe dendidi siti giidi Samotiraaqe geetettizaso bidos. Wontetha gallas Naaphule gizaso sinth hamuth gujjidos.
\v 12 Heeppeka Oroome asay tooran haarida dere gidida Maqidooniya dere waanna katama gidida Piliphisiyoose geetettizaso gelidos. Heenka undena wode uttidos.
\p 
\v 13 Sambata gallas woossa woossizaso koyishe katama gelizaso penge kezidi duge shaafa wodhdhos; nu heen uttidi shiiqi diza macasas qaala yootidos.
\v 14 Qaala lo7ethi siyiza macasatappe issi Lidiya geetettizara izakka Xoosse goynzaronne Tiyaxiroone katamappe yaada zo7o Hare may7o zal7izaro Phawuloosi yootiza qaala iza woznan wotha siyana mala Goday izi wozna doyides.
\v 15 Izanne iziso asaykka xammaqettidappe guye iza ista ta Xoosse ammanidi inte tumu erida gidikko ha taso yiidi guutha wode diishshite gaada ista mintha woossadus.
\s1 Phawuloosinne Sillassi qasho keeththan
\p 
\v 16 Issi gallas nu woossaso bishin kayo kayotta marotza issi garade naa dizaara nuna demmadus. Izakka ba maroteththan bana ayssizaytas daro miish gelthawus.
\v 17 Hanna garade naya Phawuloosanne nuna kaalla kaalla “Hayti asati intes inte attana oge yootizayti wogga Xoossa oosanchata” ga ga waassadus.
\v 18 Hessaka daro gallas shira shira gadus. Gido attin Phawuloosi ha Izi qaalan daro metotida gish izikko simmidi izi duunara haasayiza tuna ayanaza “Ne izippe kezana mala ta nena Goda Yesus Kirstoosa sunthan azazays” gides. He ayanay heerakka yeggi izippe kezides.
\p 
\v 19 Izo ayssiza asati istas miishe demmiza ogey duuxxin ista ufayssi qanxettidayssi istas gelin Phawuloosanne Silase oykkidi biittara goochchidi waannati dizaso giya giddo efida.
\v 20 Dere ayssiza waannatakko shiishshidi “Hayti asati baas Ayhuda as gidi uttidi nu katama bulakketes;
\v 21 qasse nu Oroome asati ekkanas woykko ooththanas nuus bessonta woga nu asa giddon laalettes” gida.
\p 
\v 22 Dereyka issi bolla gididi Phawuloosa bollanne Sillase bolla dendides. Deraa ayssizayti Phawuloosanta may7o qaari ekkidi durqara qoxana mala azazida.
\v 23 Iita buka bukkidi gede qasho keeththan yeggida. Qasho keeththa naagizayssika ista lo7ethi naagana mala azazida.
\v 24 Izikka hessa mala mino azazo ekkidi qasho keeththas waanna giddo kifile gelthidi ista toho gita durumara shiishshi qachides.
\p 
\v 25 Giddi gidoth gidishin Phawuloosinne Sillassi woossaninne mazamuren Xoossa galatishin qasho asay ista yethanne galata ezgi siyides.
\v 26 Hassa7ay baynda dingate qasho keeththa xaphoppe qaathiza mino biitta qaathi hanides; heerakka qasho keeththa pengeti doyettida. Qashetida ubba asa qashoy birshettides.
\v 27 Qasho keeththa naagizayssi dhiskofe beeggidi qasho keeththa pengeti doya dizayssa beyidi qasho asay wuri kessi ekkida misatin bana wodhana mashsha shoddides.
\v 28 Phawuloosi qas ba qaala dhoqu histidi “Nu wuri haan doos! Ne bolla ayne iita ooththofa” gi waassides.
\p 
\v 29 Qasho keeththa nagizayssi xompe woossi ekkidi gede giddo guppi gelides; kokkorshe Phawuloosa toho bollanne Sillase toho bolla kundides.
\v 30 Ista ekki kare kezidi “Ha asato! Ta attana mala ay ooththoo?” gides.
\p 
\v 31 Istika izas “Goda Yesusa ammana; nekka neso asaykka inte wuri attana” gida.
\v 32 Hessafe guye izassinne izason diza asas ubbas Goda qaala yootida.
\v 33 Qasho keeththa naagizayssi heerakka he gallas qamara efidi ista maduntha meecides. Heerakka izinne izaso asay wuri xaamaqetida.
\v 34 Qasho keeththa naagizayssika ista ba keeththe efidi istas kath aaththides. Baso asa ubbara Xoossa ammanida gish addezi daro ufayides.
\p 
\v 35 Gadey wontishin dere ayssizayti “Heyta asata birsha yedda” giidi ba shuumeta qasho keeththa naagizayssako yeddida.
\v 36 Qasho keeththa naagizayssika istas “Dere ayssizayti inte birshettana mala azazida; hessa gish ha7i saron kezi biite” giidi Phawuloosas yootides.
\v 37 Phawuloosi qas “Nu Oroome yeleteth gidishin pirday baynda dere sinthan durqara bukkidinne qasho keeththan yeggida. Histin ha7i qas nuna qotara asi eronta kessana koyizoo? Hessi hanenna; isti yiidi barka birshetto!” gides.
\p 
\v 38 Shuumeti he izi gida qaala dere ayssizaytas yootida istika Phawuloosinne Sillassi Oroome yeletta gididayssa siydi daggammida.
\v 39 Yiidi istafe maareteth oychidi woyneppe kessida. Isti he katamayo aggidi haraso baana mala ista woossida.
\p 
\v 40 Phawuloosinne Sillassi qasho keeththafe kezidi Lidiyaso bida. Henka diza ammanizayti ista daro minthethidi heeppe kezi bida.
\c 17
\s1 Phawuloosinne Sillassi Tasolonqen
\p 
\v 1 Phawuloosinne Sillassi Anfiphoolanne Apholooniya geetettiza derera aadhdhidi Tasolonqe geetettiza dere bida. Henka Ayhudata Woosa Keeththi dees.
\v 2 Phawuloosikka izas dose gidida mala Ayhudata Woosa Keeththe gelides. Heedzdzu saaminta kumeth qaalappe ekki ekki istara haasayettides.
\v 3 Kirstoosi waaye ekkanassinne hayqqi dendanas bessizayssa qoncisi ammanthon “Hayssi ta sabakiza Yesusi izi kiitetti yaana geetettidayssakko!” gides.
\v 4 Ayhudatappe issi issi asay ba siyidayssa ammanidi Phawuloosaranne Sillasera issife gidides. Qasseka daro derey Xoosse babbiza Giriketappe daro eretida macasati ba siyida qaalan ammanidi istara issino gidida.
\p 
\v 5 Ayhudati qasse ista qanatidi giyan diza wordo asata shiishshidi kumetha dereza ista bolla dentheththidi kataman shiro medhdhida. Phawuloosanne Sillase shiishshidi deraa sinthan essanas issi Iyaasoone geetettizayssaso koyanas elleli bida.
\v 6 Gido attin ista Iyasoone keeththan demmoonta aggida gish Iyaasoonenne hara ammaniza asata katama daannata sinthara goochchishe “Hayti asati dere wursi bul7akki ka7iishe gam7idi qasse ha7i ha yida.
\v 7 Iyaasooneyka ista ba keeththan woththides. Hayti asati wuri ‘Yesusa geetettiza hara kawoy dees’ giidi Qeesare woga ekketenna” gishe waassida.
\v 8 Dereynne he katama daannati hessa siydi ba giddon buqqettida.
\v 9 Iyaasoonenne harataka waase xeygisidi yeddida.
\s1 Phawuloosinne Sillassi Beeriyan
\p 
\v 10 Ammanizayti heerakka Phawuloosanne Sillase qammara Beeriya yeddida. Istika he gakkida mala Ayhudata Woosa Keeththe gelida.
\v 11 Beeriya asay Tasolonqe asaappe aadhdhidi akeekara diza asa. Gaasoyka hayssi yo7ozi tumeshaa? gi giidi Geeeshsha Maxaafata qaala wontin wontin pilgi xeelidi ufayssan ekkides.
\v 12 Hessa gish istafe daro asay ammanides. Qasseka istara qoodan daroti bonchettida Girike dere macasatinne addetikka ammanida.
\p 
\v 13 Tasolonqen diza Ayhuda asati Phawuloosi Xoossa qaala Beeriyanka sabakizayssa erida mala dereza dentheththanas qasseka gede istako bida.
\v 14 He wode ammanzayti Phawuloosa ellesidi gede abba achchi yeddida. Sillasinne Ximtoossi heen attida.
\v 15 Phawuloosa moyizida asati iza Atena gaththida. Qasseka Sillassiinne Ximtoossi izakko elleeli gakkana mala giza kiita Phawuloosappe ekkidi simmida.
\s1 Phawuloosi Atenan
\p 
\v 16 Phawuloosi Atenan ista naagishin Atena kataman eeqati kumidayssa beyidi daro shenetides.
\v 17 Hessa gish Ayhudata Woosa Keeththan Ayhudataranne Xoossas yayyiza Girike asara qasseka giyay dizason gallas gallas banara gaggiza asara haasayettides.
\v 18 Efiqoroosenne Istoykko geetettiza eranchata bagga gididayti Phawuloosakko shiiqidi izara haasayettida Istafe issi issi asati “Hayssi lom7u lom7ay ay gaana koyizee?” gida. Baggati qasse Yesusa gishshinne hayqoppe iza dentha mishiraachcho izi sabakishin siydi “Heyssi hara ooratha eeqata gish yootiza misatees” gida.
\p 
\v 19 Iza oykkidi Ariosfaagoose geetettiza dere duulata sinth efidi “Ha ne tamarsiza ooratha timirtey azzakkonne nu erana mala ne koyay?” gida.
\v 20 Qasse ne nuna nu haythan sisiza yo7oy nu eronta oorath gidida gish izi azzakkonne nu erana koyoos.
\v 21 Atena asay kumeth qasseka haan diza hara dere asaykka baas wode aaththanas ooratha yo7o haasayaninne sissan attin hara miishan aaththettenna.
\p 
\v 22 Hessa gish Phawuloosi Ariyosfaagoose geetettiza duulatan shiiqida dereza sinthan eqqidi “Hayto Atena asato! Inte beetto miish wursi ammanizayta gididayssa ta beyays.
\v 23 Ta yaane ha yuuyishin inte istas gooynniza miishata ta xeellishin ‘Eretonta Xoosse’ geetetti xaafetidayssa issi yarshoso demmadis; hessa gish hessa inte eronta gooyinnizayssa ta intena erissana.
\v 24 Hayssa alamezanne iza giddonka dizayssa wursi medhdhida Xoossi izi salonne sa7a Goda. Hessa gish izi asa kushen keexxettida keeththan deenna.
\v 25 Izi asa ubbas de7onne shempo; qasseka hara wursi immizayssa gidida gish izas paccizazi doonta gish izi asa kusheppe maado ekkenna.
\v 26 Asa zeereth wursi issadefe medhidi asi biitta bolla daana mala ooththides; asay daana wodenne wursetha dhas woththides.
\v 27 Hessika asi Xoosse koydinne pilgidi demmanakkonne giidi woththides; hessi hessa gidikkokka izi nuuppe issi issadefe haakki diza gish gidenna.
\v 28 Nu de7o demmiday, dizaynne qaaxetizay izanna; inte deren yeth kessiza issi issi asati ‘Nukka iza nayta’ gida mala.
\p 
\v 29 “Histikko nu Xoossa nayta gidikko Xoossi asa erateththan medhi kessida worqa woykko bira woykko shuch misatees giidi nu qoppanas bessenna.
\v 30 Kasetidi Xoossi hayssa mala hanota asay eronta ooththidayssa dandayan aadhdhides; ha7i gidikko asi wuri ba dizason dizason maarotethan gelana mala azazees” gides.
\v 31 Izi ba doosiddadde baggara biitta bolla xillotethan pirdana gallas bare woththides. Izakka hayqoppe denthidi asa ubbas hayssa tumatetha erissides.
\p 
\v 32 Istika hayqqidayta dentha gish siyida mala issi issi asati iza qidhida; baggati qas “Hayssa qasseka neeppe hara gallas siyana koyoos” gida.
\v 33 Heerakka Phawuloosi ista giddofe kezi bides.
\v 34 Issi issi asati qasse Phawuloosa kaallidanne ammanida; heytappeka Diyonassiyoosa geetettiza Ariyosfaagoose duulata keeththa Abaale gidida Demarisso geetettiza macasayanne haratikka issife deettes.
\c 18
\s1 Phawuloosi Qorontoosen
\p 
\v 1 Hessafe guye Phawuloosi Atenappe dendidi Qorontoose katama bides.
\v 2 Henka Phanxoosan yeeletida Aqqila geetettiza Ayhuda as demmides; izikka Ayhudati wuri Oroomeppe kezana mala Qalawodoosa geetettiza Oroome kawoy azazida mala ba macheyo Phirsiqillara mata wode Ixaaliya dereppe yidayssa beyanas Phawuloosi he istako bides.
\v 3 Izikka istaththo dunkane sikkizade gidida gish ista achchan uttidi dunkane sikkon gelides.
\v 4 Sambata Sambata gallas Ayhudata Woosa Keeththan ayuhudetaranne Girike asatara hasayetishe ista ammanthanas baaxetides.
\p 
\v 5 Sillassinne Ximtoossi Maqidooniyappe duge izakko wodhdhin Phawuloosi sabakon minnidi Yesusi izi Kirstoosa gididayssa Ayhudatas markattides.
\v 6 Gido attin isti izara eqqetidi iza cayida gish Phawuloosi ba may7o qoqofidi “Ta intefe xillo; inte pirdettanay inte mooron gidida gish ta inte suutha gomen oyshetikke; hessa gish ta gede Ayzaabetakko bays” gides.
\p 
\v 7 Heeppe kezidi Titoosa Iyosxoosa geetettiza Xoosse woossizayssaso bides; he addeza keeththay Ayhudata Woosa Keeththa achchan dees.
\v 8 Ayhudata Woosa Keeththa halaqay Qerisphoossi baso asa ubbara Goda ammanides; Phawuloosi yootishin siyida daro Qorontoose katama asay ammanidi xaammaqeetides.
\p 
\v 9 Goday qaman ajjutan Phawuloosa “Babbofa; Yoota; co7u gooppa;
\v 10 ta nenara days; oonikka ne bolla dendi nena qohanas dandayenna; hanno ha katamayn taas daro asi dees” gides.
\p 
\v 11 Hessa gish Phawuloosi Xoossa qaala asa tamarsishe issi laythinne bagga istara uttides.
\p 
\v 12 Galyoosa geetettiza dere ayssizayssi Akaayan diza wode Ayhudati issife gididi Phawuloosa bolla dendida; pirda wombora sinth shiishshidi,
\v 13 “Hayssi addezi wogappe karera asay Xoossas goynnana mala asa baleththees” gida.
\p 
\v 14 Phawuloosi haasayana buro duuna doyishin Galyoossi Ayhudata “Inteno Ayhuda asato! Inte shiishida yo7oy dere dentheththo woykko dere gita meton yeggiza yo7o gididakko ta woznappe siyanashin.
\v 15 Gido attin inte palamay issi issi qaalata gishshinne issi issi sunthata gish qasseka inte woga gishas gidida gish inte heen inte baggara wursite; ta hessa mala yo7o pirdanas koyikke” gides.
\v 16 Hessa gish pirda wombora sinthafe ista kessides.
\v 17 He wode wurikka Ayhuda Woosa Keeththa halaqa Sostineese geetettizayssa oykkidi pirda keeththa sinthan bukkida; Galyoossi gidikko hessa wudanka yeggibenna.
\s1 Phirsiqilla Aqilanne Aphilosa
\p 
\v 18 Hessafe guye Phawuloosi Qorontoose kataman daro wode gam7ides. Heeppeka ammaniza asay moyzin Phirsiqillaranne Aqilara issife markaben gelidi Sooriya geetettizaso bides; adina dizayssa gaththanas Kinkira7oose geetettizason ba hu7e meedettides. \f + \fr 18:18 \fq adina gizayssa issi issi bagga Gamoththo qaalan “Tasala woykko galatas imettiza imota” geettes.\f*\x * \xo 18:18 \xt Tay 6:18\x*
\v 19 Efesoone gakkida mala Phirsiqillanne Aqila heen aggagidi Phawuloosi Ayhudata Woosa Keeththe gelidi Ayhudatara haasayettides.
\v 20 Banara gam7ana mala isti oychin izi “Akay” giidi ixxides.
\v 21 Gido attin izi istafe shaaketishe “Xoossa shene gidikko ta simmada yaana” gides; Efesooneppe dendidi markaben gelidi bides.
\p 
\v 22 Qisaariya geetettizaso gakkidappe guye kezidi ammanizayta saro giidi heeppe Anxokiya wodhdhides.
\v 23 Anxokkiyan guuththa wode takkidappe guye heeppe dendidi Galatiya baggaranne Firgiya geetettiza deretara yuuy aadhdhidi ammanzayta minthethides.
\p 
\v 24 He wode issi Iskindiriya kataman yeletida Aphilosa geetettiza issi Ayhuda asi Efesoone yides; izikka tamaridadenne Geeshsha Maxaafata lo7ethi erizade.
\v 25 Izi Goda oge tamaridadenne Yesusa gish balay baynda haasayizadenne Xillo Ayanan xuugetishe tamarsizade; gido attin izi lo7ethi erizay Yohannisa xinqate xalala.
\v 26 Izikka Ayhuda Woosa Keeththan babbonta yooto oykkides; Phirsiqillaynne Aqqilay izi gizayssa siydinne iza gede baso efidi Xoossa oge iza kaseppe lo7ethi erissida.
\p 
\v 27 Aphilossi gede Akaaya baanas koyin ammanizayti iza minthethida; heen diza ammaniza asaykka iza mokki ekkana mala izas dabdaabe xaafida; izi he gakkida mala izas diza immotappe dendidayssan ammanizayta daro maaddizade gidides.
\v 28 Geeshsha Maxaafata yayssa hayssara gaththi markasi markasi Yesusi izi Kirstoosa gididayssa Ayhudatara daro palametidi dere sinthan ista laththides.
\c 19
\s1 Phawuloosi Efesoonen
\p 
\v 1 Aphilossi Qorontoosen diza wode Phawuloosi pudeha bagga derera kanthidi Efesoone yiidi heen diza issi issi ammaniza asata demmidi
\v 2 “Inte ammanida wode Xillo Ayana ekkideti?” gides; Istika “Ekkibeykko haray attoshin Xillo Ayanay dizaakkonne nu sibeykko” gida.
\p 
\v 3 Phawuloosikka ista “Histin inte aazan xammaqetidetii?” gides; Istika izas “Yohannisa xinqatan xammaqetidos” gida.
\p 
\v 4 Phawuloosikka istas “Yohannisa xinqatay gidikko asay maarotethan simmidayssa bessiza xinqatakko! Yohannisi ba baggara asay izappe guyera yiza Yesusa ammanana mala yootides” gides. \x * \xo 19:4 \xt Mato 3:11; Mar 1:4,7,8; Luqa 3:4,16; Yoha 1:26-27\x*
\p 
\v 5 Istika hessa siyidappe guye Goda Yesusa sunthan xammaqetida.
\v 6 Phawuloosikka ista bolla ba kushe woththida mala Xillo Ayanay ista bolla wodhdhin isti dumma dereta qaalara haasayida; tinbitekka yootida.
\v 7 He asati wurikka tammanne nam7u gidizayta.
\p 
\v 8 Phawuloosi Ayhudata Woosa Keeththe gelidi Xoossa Kawoteththa gish hasayettishenne ista ammanthishe heedzdzu agina kumeth oonaska babbonta asaas qoncisi yootides.
\v 9 Issi issi asay palama xin7i giidi ammananas koybenna; Goda oge qonccen ixida; hessa gish Phawuloosi ista aggidi haraso bides; ammanizaytaka dumma shaakki kessidi Xiranoose timirte keeththan gallas gallas istara haasayettides.
\v 10 Hessa mala ooson nam7u layth gam7ida gish Iisiya awurajjan diza Ayhudatinne Girike asay wuri Goda qaala siyana dandayides.
\p 
\v 11 Xoossi Phawuloosa baggara daro malalisiza malata ooththides.
\v 12 Maarabe woykko iza asateth bochchida carqa efidi harganchata bochchikko hargey yeddees; tuna ayanatikka ba oykkida asappe kezeettes.
\v 13 Yuuyi yuuyi asappe daydanthi kessiza issi issi Ayhuda asati “Phawuloosi sabakiza Yesusa sunthan inte kezana mala azazays” giidi Goda suntha tuna ayanati oykkida asata bolla xeeygana paacida.
\v 14 Issi Ayhudatappe gidida Qeeseta halaqa Asqewes attuma naa laapunati hessatho ooththida.
\p 
\v 15 Tuna ayanaykka “Ta Yesusakka erays; Phawuloosakka erays shin inte qas oonantee?” gides.
\p 
\v 16 Qasseka tuna ayanay iza oykkidadey guppidi asata oykkides; ista bolla wolqatidi daro minnin madunxidi keeththafe mela kaallo baqatida.
\v 17 Hessika Efesoonen diza Ayhudata achchaninne Girike asa ubba achchan eretin wurikka babbida; hessanka Goda Yesusa sunthi bonchettides.
\v 18 Ammanida asappe daroy shiiqidi ba iita ooso qoncen paaxides.
\v 19 Maro marotizaytappe daroti ba marotiza maxaafa shiishshidi dere sinthan taman xuugida; maxaafa waagay shiishshi qoodin ichashu tammu shi bira mala gidides.
\v 20 Hayssa malan Goda qaalay keehi diccishenne xooni xooni bides.
\p 
\v 21 Hayssi wuri hanidappe guye Phawuloosi Maqidooniyaranne Akaaya baggara aadhdhidi Yerusalame baanas qofa qachidi “Ta he gakkidappe guye ta Oroome qasseka beyana koshshees” gides.
\v 22 Bana maaddizaytappe nam7ata Ximtoosanne Erisxoosa gede Maqidooniya geetettizaso kiittidi baas Iisiya awurajjan guutha wode heen de7ides.
\s1 Efesoonen dendida shiiro
\p 
\v 23 He wode Goda oge gish daro shiroy medhetides.
\v 24 Dimexiroosa geetettiza issi bira qoxizayssi Arxemise geetettiza eeqa misile birappe seeris medhi medhi hiillanchatas wodhe miishe demmises.
\v 25 Izikka he hiillanchatan hessa mala ooson aqizayta hara asata issi bolla shiishshidi “Aso! Hayssi oosozi nuus miish kessizayssa inte ereeta;
\v 26 hayssi Phawuloosa geetettizayssi Efesoonen xalla gidonta kumeththa Iisiya awurajjan diza daro dereza ammanthi ammanthi baleththizayssa inte wurikka beyizayssa malanne siyizayssa mala ‘Asa kushen oosettida eeqati mulekka Xoosse gidetenna’ gi yootees.
\v 27 Hayssa nu oosozas lo7o suntha hiraayssizayssafe bollara kumeththa Iisiyaynne kumeththa alamey gooynniza wogga Arxemisse eeqa keeththaykka go7ay bayndayssa gidana; qasseka keehi dhoqu gida izi bonchoykka kawuyana” gides.
\p 
\v 28 Asay hessa siydi iita hanqo hanqettidi “Efesoone Arxemissa wogga gita!” giidi waasso doommides.
\v 29 Heerakka kumeththa katamay shirotides; dereyka wuri issi bolla gididi Maqidooniya asa gididaytanne Phawuloosara issife yuuyiza iza laggeta Gayiyoosanne Arisxirokoosa oykkidi derey kase ka7izaso wothan gelida.
\v 30 Phawuloosikka kare kezidi asa sinth shiiqana koyin ammanizayti diggida.
\v 31 He awurajja daannatappe issi issi Phawuloosa laggeti Phawuloosi asay kase ka7izaso xalidi gellonta mala as kiittidi woossida.
\p 
\v 32 Shiiqida asay un7etidi issadey issi miish haasayishin haray qas hara hasayessinne asay wuri waassetes; dariza bagga asay aazas heen shiiqidakkonne erenna.
\v 33 Ayhuda asay Iskindirosa geetettizayssa deraa giddofe sugereth gede sinth kessida wode issi issi asati ba gish izi haasayana mala waassida; izikka ista gish palamettana koydi asay co7u gaana mala malati bessides.
\v 34 Gido attin izi Ayhuda as gididayssa erida wode wurikka issi bolla “Efesoone Arximissa wogga; gita!” gishe nam7u saate mala asay waassides.
\p 
\v 35 He katamas waanna xaafey asa co7u histidi “Inteno Efesoone asato! Gita Arxemisi eeqa keeththaynne saloppe wodhdhida izi misile naagizay Efesoone katama asa gididayssa erontay oonee?
\v 36 Hessa gish hayssi ha tumay kadettana dandayettontayssa mala inte guuthi yuushi qoppanassinne loddu gaanas bessees.
\v 37 Hayta asata Xoossa Keeththa bonqonta woykko nu xoosse gididayssa bolla cashsha qaala denthonta dishin inte oykkidi ha gaththanas coo ehideta.
\p 
\v 38 “Hessa gish Dimoxiroossinne izara diza bira seerisi ooththiza hiillanchati oona bollaka mootiza yo7oy diikko pirda keeththay istas doya dees; daannatikka deettes; koyidade mootanas dandayees.
\v 39 Hayssafe hara gaanas inte koykko wogay diza shiiqoson beyetto.
\v 40 Hessi attikko hach hanida shiroy nuna mootisonta mala hirgisees; mootos gathiza gaasoy baynda gish ha hanida shiroza gish nu oyshetikko gaanazi nuus deenna” gides.
\v 41 Izi hessa gidappe guye shiiqoy laalettides.
\c 20
\s1 Phawuloosi Maqidooniyanne Girike bides
\p 
\v 1 Asay co7u gidappe guye Phawuloosi ammanizayta issi bolla xeygidi ista minthethiza qaalara zoridappe guye ista sarokidi Maqidooniya baana kezides.
\v 2 Izi aadhdhi biza deren diza ammaniza asa lo7eth zoren minthethishe Girike dere bides.
\v 3 Giriken heedzdzu agina takkidappe guye markabera Sooriya geetettiza dere baanas qoppides shin Ayhuda asati iza bolla iita ooththana zoretidayssa eridi Maqidooniya baggara baana qofa qachides.
\p 
\v 4 Beeriyappe Phariyoosa naa Sophaxiroosa, Tasolonqefe Arisxirokoosanne Sikondoosa, Derbeeneppe Gayiyoossinne Ximtoossi Iisiyappe Xirofimoossinne Tiqiqoossi Phawuloosara issife bida.
\v 5 Heyti wuri nuuppe kasetidi Xiro7aadan nuna naagida.
\v 6 Nu qas uketha ba7aaleppe guye Piliphisiyooseppe markaben isti dizaso Xiro7aada geetettizaso ichashantha gallas gakkidi heen laapun gallas gam7idos.
\s1 Phawuloosi wursethan Xiro7aada beydes
\p 
\v 7 Saamintafe koyro wogga gallas issife kath maanas nu shiiqi dishin Phawuloosi wonto baanas koshshiza gish shiiqida asas qaala yootishin izi yo7oza leela gidoth gakkanaas adussides. \f + \fr 20:7 \ft “Saamintafe koyro gallassan” Qeera omars woggay wontanawu guussa.\f*
\v 8 Bolla fooqen daro poo7oy dizason nu shiiqidos.
\v 9 Awuxekise geetettiza issi natetha nay maskote bolla utti dishin Phawuloosi yo7oza adussidayssafe dendidayssan iza dhiskoy ekki bides; wolqama dhiskon xoonetidi bolla heedzdzantho fooqeppe duge kundin asay denthiza wode hayqqidi beettides.
\v 10 Gido attin Phawuloosi duge wodhdhidi naaza bolla hokki idimmidinne “Hayqibenna paxa dees, daggammofte!” gides.
\v 11 Phawuloosi hessafe pude fooqe kezidi uketha menthidi ammanizaytara mides; gadey wontana gakkanaas asatara hasayettishe gam7idi bides.
\v 12 Asaykka hayqoppe paxida naaza gede izaso efidi wurikka ufayetides.
\s1 Phawuloosi Xiro7adafe Milixine geetettizaso bides
\p 
\v 13 Nu Phawuloosa Markaben gelthana koyda gish kasetidi markaben Asosa geetettizaso bidos; nu hessa ooththiday Phawuloosi Asosa gakkanaas tohora baana koyda gishassinne nu gede sinth baana mala izi azazida gishassa.
\v 14 Nu izara Asosan gaaggidi izi markaben gelin izara issife Mixiline bidos.
\v 15 Wontetha gallas heeppe dendidi sinthara diza Ki7oose geetettizaso gakkidos; qasse wontetha gallas Saamoose geetettizaso pinnidi heeppe wontetha gallas Miliixe gakkidos.
\v 16 Phenxaqoste geetettiza Ayhudata Paaziga ba7aale baas dandayettida mala bonchana Yerusalamen bettana koydi izi Iisiyan wodey aadhdhonta dishin Efesoone aadhdhi baanas koydes. Iisiyan izas wodey aadhdhonta mala Efesoone yeggi aadhdhana koyides. Izi hessatho ooththana koyiday Phenxaqoste ba7aales Yerusalamen bettanas koyda gishassa.
\s1 Phawuloosi Efesoone Woosa Keeththa cimatara wursetha moyzo saroka sarokettides
\p 
\v 17 Phawuloosi Miliixeppe Efesoone Woosa Keeththa cimata ase kiittidi xeygisides.
\v 18 Istika yiin Phawuloosi ista “Ta Iisiya gelida gallassafe ha simmin ubba wode ta intenara waana waana de7idakkonne inte ereeta.
\v 19 Ayhudati ta bolla asa denthidi hilida geedon daro metoy ta bolla gakkikkoka ta kumeththa ashketetharanne afunthara Godas ooththadis. Coo denbanka inte inteson ta intena tamarsashe go7izayssa wursa intes yootadis attin intena go7iza miishafe aykkokka ashshabekke.
\v 20-21 Ayhuda asata gidinka Girike asa gidinka maarotethan gelidi Xoossako simmana malanne Goda Yesusan ammanana mala lo7etha yootadis.
\p 
\v 22 “Ha7ikka ta he gakkishin ta bolla aazi gakkanakkonne erikeshin Xillo Ayanay tana azazida mala Yerusalame bays.
\v 23 Heen dumma dumma tana qashoynne metoy naagizayssa Xillo Ayanay taas yootides.
\v 24 Gido attin Goda Yesusi taas immida wotha woxxa wursana gakkanaassinne ooso ta polana gakkanaas tani ta shempos mishetikke; taas imettida oosoykka Xoossa mishiraachcho qaala yootokko. \x * \xo 20:24 \xt 2Xim 4:7\x*
\p 
\v 25 “Ha7i gakkanaas ta inte giddon simeretashe Xoossa kawoteth sabakadis; Sima hayssafe guye intefe oonnikka mule ta ayfeso beyontayssa ta erays.
\v 26 Hessa gish intefe issadeykka dhaykko ta oyshetontayssa hach ta intena erisays.
\v 27 Ayssi giikko ta Xoossa qofa wursa intes yootadis attin aykkokka ta yootonta ashshidayssi deenna.
\v 28 Xillo Ayanay intena Xoossa dorsata heemmanas shuumides; hessa gish inte hu7essinne Xoossa dorsatas naagetite; Goday ba suuthan wozida Woosa Keeththayo naagite.
\v 29 Ta bidappe guye Xoossa dorsatas michetonta iita asati inte gars gellanayssa ta erays.
\v 30 Hessathoka issi issi asati inte giddofe dendidi geella yo7o intena tamarsidi ammaniza asappe darota gede baako zaarana.
\v 31 Hessa gish intena issa issa heedzdzu layth qammanne gallas afunxa zoridayssa yuushi qoppitenne naagetite.
\p 
\v 32 “Ha7ikka intena Xoossas minthi essanassinne ammanizayta giddon intes laataso immanas dandayiza iza aadho kiyatetha qaalas ta hadara immadis.
\v 33 Ta oona birakka worqa woykko may7o ammotabekke.
\v 34 Ta ta kushen ooththa ooththada taas maaddetada tanara dizayitaka maaddidayssa inteka ereeta.
\v 35 ‘Ha ekkizadefe gede immizadey anjetidade’ giza Goda Yesusa qaala nu yuushi qoppidi nurka nu kushera nu ooththi demmidi hara daaburanchata gede maaddanas nuus bessizayssa ta intena daro dumma dumma ogera besadis” gides.
\p 
\v 36 Hessafe guye Phawuloosi ubba asara gulbatidi woossides.
\v 37 Asay wuri yeekkidi Phawuloosa idimmi oykkidi yeerides.
\v 38 Harappeka isti daro mishetiday izi “Hayssafe guyen inte nam7antho tana beyekketa” gida gishassa; heeppeka iza markabekko gakkanaas moyzida.
\c 21
\s1 Phawuloosi Yerusalame bides
\p 
\v 1 Nu istafe shaaketidinne markaben gelidi siti giidi Qoose geetettiza abba giddon diza dere bidos; wontetha gallas hara Erodoose geetettiza abba giddon diza dere gakkidos. Heeppeka issi Phaxira geetettiza katama bidos.
\v 2 Heen gede Pinqe geetettizaso biza markabe dizaaro demmidinne izin gelidi bidos.
\v 3 Abba giddon diza Qophiroose geetettiza dereppe hadirsa baggan yeggidi Sooriya geetettiza dere biidi Xiroose geetettiza abba achchan diza dere bidos; hessas gaasoy markabeya ba caanettida caana heen wothanas koshshiza gishassa.
\v 4 Heen ammanzayta koyi demmidi istara laappun gallas gam7idos; istika Xillo Ayana kaalethon Phawuloosa “Yerusalame booppa” giidi yootida.
\v 5 Nu heen gam7ana wodey wurin istafe shaaketidi nu oge bidos. Isti wuri ba machetaranne ba naytara issife katamappe kare kezana gakkanaas nuna moyizida; abba achchan nu wuri gulbatidi woossidappe guye dendidi issoy issara saroketidi shaaketidos.
\v 6 Hessafe guye nu markaben gelin isti gede baso simmida.
\p 
\v 7 Nu Xirooseppe dendidi gede Phixilamaysse geetettizaso gakkidos. Henka ammaniza asara gaggidi saroketidi heen ista achchan issi gallas gam7idos.
\v 8 Wontetha gallas heeppe kezidi Qisaariya geetettizaso bidos; Qisaariyan laapun daaqonetappe issa wongelaawe Philphoosaso gelidi iza achchan shempidos. \x * \xo 21:8 \xt Hawa 6:5; 8:5\x*
\v 9 Izas nabe gidida oyddu gelonta geella7o nayti deettes.
\p 
\v 10 Daro gallas nu heen gam7in issi Agaboossa geetettiza nabey Yuhuda dereppe yides.
\v 11 He nabey nuukko shiiqidinne Phawuloosa danco ekkidi ba tohonne ba kushe qachidi “Xillo Ayanay hayssa dancaa goda Yerusalamen diza Ayhuda asati hayssatho qachidi Ayzaabetas aaththi immana gees” gides.
\p 
\v 12 Hessa siydi nukka nunara diza asaykka Phawuloosi Yerusalame boonta mala woossidos.
\v 13 Qas Phawuloosi “Inte aysi yeekki yeekkidi ta wozna aazas menthetii? Tani Goda Yesusa suntha gish Yerusalamen qasho xalala gidonta hayqqanaska giigetadis” gides.
\p 
\v 14 Izi nu zore ekkonta ixin “Histikko Goda sheney hano” giidi aggagidos.
\p 
\v 15 Nu heen guuththa gallassata gam7idappe guye nu miishe wursi giigissidi ekki Yerusalame bidos.
\v 16 Qisaariyan diza issi issi ammanzayti nunara issife yida; istika nuni Minasoone keeththan daana mala nuna izaso kaalethida; Minasooni kasetidi ammanida Qophiroose dere asa.
\s1 Phawuloosi Yerusalamen Yaqoobe beyides
\p 
\v 17 Nu Yerusalame gakkida mala ammanzayti nuna ufayssan mokki ekkida.
\v 18 Wontetha gallas Phawuloosi nunara Yaqoobekko bides; he wode Woosa Keeththa cimati heen deettes.
\v 19 Phawuloosi asa wursi sarothidappe guye Xoossi iza baggara Ayzaabeta giddon ooththidayssa wursi issino ashshonta yootides.
\p 
\v 20 Hessa siydi asay wuri Xoosse galatides; Phawuloosikka “Nu ishazo daro shiyan qoodetiza ammanizayti Ayhudata giddon dizayssanne wurikka Muse woga woznappe naagizayta gididayssa nekka eraasa.
\v 21 Neni Ayzaabeta giddon diza Ayhudata Inte nayta qaxxaroppite woykko wogata ooththofte gaada ne tamarsida asay Muse woga shaarana mala ooththes giza wore asay siydes.
\v 22 Histin ha7i aaze lo7oy? Ha7i ne yuussa asay siyonta aggenna.
\v 23 Hessa gish nu nena gizayssa ooththa; nu achchan tasala gaththana yida oyddu asati deettes. \x * \xo 21:23 \xt Tay 6:13-21\x*
\v 24 Ne ista nenara ekkada istara gidada nena geeshsha; asati ba hu7e meedettana malanne Xoossa Keeththan imettiza muxuwata miisha ne istas qanxa; ne hessatho ooththikko ne bolla woretidayssi wuri mela gididayssanne nekka Muse woga pola naagizade gididayssa asay wuri erana.
\v 25 Hinko Ayzaabetappe ammanidayta gish gidikko ‘Eeqqas shukettidi tunidayssa mooppite, suuthika uyoppite, bawuta hayqqida mehe asho mooppite, laymafe haakkite’ giidi cimati qachida qaala dabdaabe xaafidi nu istas yeddidos.” \x * \xo 21:25 \xt Hawa 15:29\x*
\p 
\v 26 Hessafe guye Phawuloosi he oyddu asata banara ekkidi wontetha gallas istara bana geeshshides; isti geeyiza gallassati aapun gallassikkonne issade issade gish imettiza miish immiza wodey aydekkonne erisanas Xoossa Keeththe gelides.
\s1 Phawuloosi Xoossa Keeththan dishe oyketides
\p 
\v 27 Laapun gallas kumana maatishin Iisiya dereppe yida Ayhuda asay Phawuloosa Xoossa Keeththan beyidi deraa iza bolla dentheththidi iza oykkida.
\v 28 “Isra7eele asato! Nuna maaddite! Nu asanne nu woga hayssa nu dizasoza cayishenne derey dizason ubban asa tamarsizayssi hayssi izakko! Hessika gidenna giidi Ayzaabeta Xoossa Keeththe gelthidi hayssa geeshsha soza tunisides” gishe waassida.
\v 29 Isti hessa gida gaasoy hayssafe kase Efesoone yeletta gidida Xirofimosa izara issife katama giddon beyida gish iza Phawuloosi Xoossa Keeththe ekki gelida misatida gishassa. \x * \xo 21:29 \xt Hawa 20:4\x*
\p 
\v 30 Kumeththa katamay ba giddon shirotides; derey wuri issife woxxi koydi Phawuloosa oykki ekkidi Xoossa Keeththa gibbefe gooshechi kessides; Xoossa Keeththa pengeti heerakka gordettida.
\v 31 Asay Phawuloosa wodhana koyishin “Yerusalame diza kumeththa derey ba giddon shirotides” giza kiitay Oroome wotadarata azazizayssakko gakkides.
\v 32 Hessa gish izi wotadaratanne mato halaqata kaaleththidi eeson woxxishe asay dizaso bides; asay olanchata azazizayssa beyidi Phawuloosa buka aggida.
\p 
\v 33 Mato halaqazi izakko shiiqidi Phawuloosa oykkidi nam7u sansalatan qashettana mala azazidi izi oonakkonne ayy ooththidakone eranas iza oychides.
\v 34 Dereyka ba giddon baggay hessa, baggay hayssa gides; Mato halaqazi dereza waasoppe dendidayssan tumay awayssakonne eranas dandayettonta ixin Phawuloosa gede wotadarati dizaso efana mala azazides.
\v 35 Phawuloosi pude dhoqaso gakkishin derey daro hanqon iza bolla meto gaththanas koyda gish wotadarati iza hashen tookki efida.
\v 36 Dereyka “Izi hayqqo! Hayqqo” gi waassishe iza kaallides.
\s1 Phawuloosi bana ashshana maaddiza yo7o yootides
\p 
\v 37 Wotadarati Phawuloosa ba dizaso gelthana maatishin Phawuloosi wotadarata azazizayssa “Ta nees issi miish yootana mala dosay?” gides. Mato halaqazikka “Ne Girike qaala eray?”
\v 38 “Histin ha7i mata dere giddon meto dentheththida shempo wodhdhida oyddu shi asa ekkada bazzo baqatida Gibxe addezi nena diikkii?” gides.
\p 
\v 39 Phawuloosikka “Tani Kilqiya giddon daro eretida Xarseese kataman yeletida Ayhuda asa; hayssa asas tana yoocharki” gides.
\p 
\v 40 Izi haasayana mala ero giin Phawuloosi dhoqason eqqidi asay co7u gaana mala ba kushera malatides; asay co7u giin Isra7eeleta qaalara,
\c 22
\p 
\v 1 “Ta ishato! Ta aawato! Ta bolla wordo woththidayssas ta intes immiza zaaro siyite!”
\v 2 Izi Ayhudata qaalara haasayishin siydi kaseppe asay co7u gides; Phawuloosikka haasaya gujjidi hizgides.
\p 
\v 3 “Tani Kilqiya giddon diza Xarseese kataman yeeletida Ayhuda asa; tani dicciday gidikko hannin Yerusalamena; ta nu aawata woga wursa Gamalyaaleppe lo7etha tamaradissenne inte hach ooththizayssatho Xoossas suure woznappe ooththashe de7adis. \x * \xo 22:3 \xt Hawa 5:34-39\x*
\v 4 Hayssa ha ogeza kaalliza asata ubba wodhana gakkanaas goodaththiza asakkoshin; macatanne addeta qacha qacha qasho keeththe yeddizadekkoshin.
\v 5 Hayssi wuri tumu gididayssa Qeeseta halaqatinne dere cimatikka wuri taas markattana; haray attoshin Damasqon diza ammaniza asa qacha Yerusalame ehada qaxayssanas Damasqon dizaytas xaafetida dabdaabe Qeeseta halaqataappenne dere cimatappe ekkadis.
\s1 Phawuloosi Kirstoosa wosti ammanidakko yootides
\r (Hawa 9:1-19; 26:12-18)
\p 
\v 6 “Tani Damasqo bishininne katama gelana matishin seeta gallas ta qopponta dishin saloppe wolqama poo7oy tana yuuy aadhdhi poo7ides.
\v 7 He wode tani biitta bolla kundada Sawule! Sawule! Ne tana aazas goodday? giza qaala siyadis.
\v 8 Takka ‘Godo ne oonee?’ gadis; izikka ‘Ta neni gooddiza Naazirete Yesusa’ gides.
\v 9 Tanara issife diza asati poo7oza beyida attin izi tanara haasayishin qaala siybetenna.
\v 10 Takka ‘Godo ta ayy ooththoo?’ gadis. Godayka ‘Dendada Damasqo ba, ne ooththanayssa isti nees heen yootana’ gides.
\v 11 Poo7oza xolqetetha daroppe dendidayssan ta xeellanas dandayabekke; tanara diza asati ta kushe oykki goochchidi tana Damasqo gaththida.
\p 
\v 12 “Hananiya geetettiza issadey heen dees; Hananiyay Damasqon diza Ayhudata achchan daro galattettidayssanne woga bonchiza asa.
\v 13 Izi ta ach shiiqi eqqidi ‘Ta isha Sawule ne ayfey qasseka xeello’ gides; heerakka ta ayfey iza xeellides.
\v 14 Izikka tana ‘Nu aawanta Xoossi ne iza shene erana mala, iza xilloza ne beyana malanne izi gizayssa ne siyana mala nena kaseti doorides.
\v 15 Izi hessa ooththiday ne beyidayssanne siyidayssa asa ubba sinthan izas ne markattanassa.
\v 16 Histin ha7i aazas gam7ay? Dendada iza sunth xeeygada xammaqeta; ne nagarappekka meeceta’ gides.
\v 17 Hessafe guye ta Yerusalame simmada Xoossa keeththan woossishin ajjutay taas beettides.
\v 18 Godayka taas qoncidi ‘Ne ta gish immana markateth isti ekkonta gish ne gam7onta dashe Yerusalameppe ellela keza!’ gides.
\v 19 Takka izas ‘Godo ta Ayhudata Woosa Keeththati dizaso baada nena ammanizayta ubba qachada ista bukkidayssa ba baggara istika eretes.
\v 20 Ne gish markatiza Istifanoose asay wodhiza wode takka he wodhiza asata achchan eqqada isti wodhizayssa takka dosadissenne wodhizayta may7okka naagadis’ gides. \x * \xo 22:20 \xt Hawa 7:58\x*
\v 21 Godayka ‘Hahon diza Ayzaabetakko ta nena kiittiza gish dendada ba!’ ” gides.
\s1 Phawuloosi Oroome dere as gididayssa qoncisides
\p 
\v 22 Asay hinno gakkanaas Phawuloosa haasaya woznappe lo7ethi siyishe aggidi ba qaala dhoqu histidi “Hayssa mala asi nu biittafe dhayo; hayssa mala asi nu biittan shempora daanas bessena” gishe waassides.
\v 23 Asay waassishe ba may7o qaari qaari wuxxishenne biitta pude salo dharcides.
\v 24 Mato halaqazi hessa beyidi Phawuloosa wotadarati dizaso gelthana mala azazides; dereyka iza bolla aazas hessa mala waassizakko erana mala iza garafidi paaxisana mala azazides.
\v 25 Gido attin dafon waaxi qachidi iza garafana giigetishin Phawuloosi ba achchan eqqida issi mato halaqas “Oroome as pirday baynda garafanas intes fiiqadey dizee?” gides.
\v 26 Mato halaqay hessa siyida mala gede halaqata azazizayssakko biidi “Ay ooththana gay? hayssi addezi Oroome asakko!” gides.
\v 27 Hessa gish halaqata azazizayssi Phawuloosakko shiiqidi “Ane taas yoota, ne Oroome asee?” gides; izikka “Ee ta Oroome asa” gides.
\v 28 Azazizaysikka “Ta Oroome asa gidanas daro miishe qanxada shaamadis” giin Phawuloosi “Tani gidikko Oroomen yelettadis” gides.
\v 29 Hessa gish iza maramaranas giigettida asati heerakka iza achchafe haakkida; azazizaysikka izi Oroome as sansalatan qachidayssa yuush qoppidi babbides.
\s1 Phawuloosi Ayhudata duulata sinth shiiqides
\p 
\v 30 Wontetha gallas azazizayssi Ayhudati Phawuloosa mootiza ayfe yo7oy azakkonne eranas koyides; Qeeseta halaqatinne Ayhudata shango duulata asay wuri issadeykka attonta kumeth shiiqana mala azazides; Phawuloosakka qashoppe birshidi shiiqida asa sinth shiishshi essides.
\c 23
\p 
\v 1 Phawuloosi duulata asa tishshi histi xeelidi “Ta ishato! Hach gakkanaas ta Xoossa sinthan lo7o qofara dayssi” gides.
\v 2 Qeeseta halaqa Hananiyay qasse Phawuloosa duunan shocana mala iza achchan eqqidayta azazides.
\v 3 Heerakka Phawuloosi Hananiya “Haysso aannora tiyettida keeththazo! Nenakka Xoossi shocana; wogara pirdana uttada wogay baynda tana shocana mala azazay?” gides. \x * \xo 23:3 \xt Mato 23:27-28\x*
\p 
\v 4 He wode heen diza asay Phawuloosa “Xoossa Qeeseta halaqa cayay?” gides.
\v 5 Phawuloosikka istas “Ta ishato! Izi Qeeseta halaqa gididayssa ta erabeykke. gaasoyka ‘Ne dere halaqa bolla iita qaala gooppa’ gizayssi xaafetides” gides. \x * \xo 23:5 \xt Kessa 22:28\x*
\p 
\v 6 Phawuloosi heen diza asappe baggay Saduqaaweta, baggay Farsaaweeta gididayssa eridinne “Ta ishato! Ta Farsaaweeppe yelettadissinne; takka Farsaawe; hekko ha7i ta pirdettana shiiqiday hayqqidayti dendanayssa ta ufays ooththiza gishassa” giidi ba qaala dhoqu histidi duulata asa sinthan yootides. \x * \xo 23:6 \xt Hawa 26:5; Pili 3:5\x*
\p 
\v 7 Phawuloosi hessa yootida mala Farsaaweeta giddoninne Saduqaaweta giddonka ooshi dendin duulatay nam7u shaaketi wodhdhides.
\v 8 Gaasoyka Saduqaaweti “Hayqqidaytas denthi deenna; kiitanchaykka baawa; Ayanaykka deenna gizayta; Farsaaweeti qasse heyti wurikka deettes” gi ammanizayta. \x * \xo 23:8 \xt Mato 22:23; Mar 12:18; Luqa 20:27\x*
\p 
\v 9 Hessa wode daro shiroy asa giddon hanides; Farsaaweeta baggata gidida issi issi Muse woga tamarizayti dendidi “Nu hayssa addeza bolla aykkokka iita miish demmibekko; ayanay woykko kiitanchay izas yootida gidana; nu ay erizoni?” giidi palametida.
\p 
\v 10 Palamay minni minni bida gish asay Phawuloosa tarsherethonta mala babbidi halaqata azazizayssi “Duge wodhdhidi Phawuloosa asa giddofe ha kessi ekki yiidi gede wotadarati dizaso efite!” giidi wotadarata halaqata azazides.
\v 11 Wontetha gallas leela gidoth Goday Phawuloosa achchan eqqidi “Aykkoy ba ne Yerusalamen taas markattidayssatho Oroomenka ne taas markattanas bessees” gides.
\s1 Phawuloosa wodhanas asay maqetides
\p 
\v 12 Gadey wontin Ayhuda asati shiiqetidi “Nu Phawuloosa wodhonta dishe kath mookko; haathika uyokko” gi caaqettida.
\v 13 Hessa he maqozan issife gidida asa qooday oyddu tammafe bollara dees.
\v 14 Istika Qeeseta halaqatakkonne dere cimatakko biidi istas “Nu Phawuloosa wodhonta dishe kath moonta mala minthi caaqidos.
\v 15 Hessa gidida gish inte dere cimatara zoretidi iza keehi marammariza misatidi isti intes Phawuloosa ehana mala azazizayssa oychite; nukka izi ha hanno gakkanappe kasetidi iza wodhana giigettidos” gida.
\p 
\v 16 Gido attin issi Phawuloosas michi nay hessa ista maqoza siyida gish wotadarati dizaso bi geellidi yo7oza Phawuloosas yootides.
\v 17 Phawuloosikka Mato halaqatappe issa baako xeygidi “Hayssi naazi wotadarata azazizayssas yootiza yo7oy diza gish gede izakko efa” gides.
\v 18 Mato halaqay naaza waana azazizayssakko ekki geellidi “Qashetida Phawuloosi tana baako xeygidi hayssi naazi nees yootiza yo7oy diza gish ta iza neekko shiishana mala tana woossides” gides.
\p 
\v 19 Azazizaysikka naaza kushe oykki ekkidi haraso pooqidi “Ne taas yootanayssi aazee?” giidi iza dumma oychides.
\p 
\v 20 Naazikka “Ayhuda asati Phawuloosa yo7oza lo7ethi maaramarizade misatissidi wonto ne iza istas shiishana mala oychanas qachi woththida.
\v 21 Gido attin ne istas ero gooppa; gaasoyka ‘Nu iza wodhonta dishe kath mokko haathika uyokko’ giidi caaqqettidayti oyddu tammafe bolla gidiza asi iza wodhanas oge bolla zugges; ha7i isti naagizay ne zaaro xalala” gides.
\p 
\v 22 Azazizaysikka “Ne hayssa taas yootidayssa hara oonakka erissofa” giidi naaza moyizides.
\s1 Phawuloosi dere haariza Filkise sinth shiiqides
\p 
\v 23 Hessafe guye wotadarata azazizayssi mato halaqatappe nam7ata xeygidi “Qammafe heedzdzu saate gidishin Qisaariya geetettizaso bana mala nam7u xeetu wotadarata, laapun tammu toganchatanne nam7u xeetu toora asa giigissite;
\v 24 Phawuloosasikka para giigissidi dere haariza Filkisekko lo7on gakkana mala ooththite” gides.
\p 
\v 25 Dabdabe hizgi xaafides;
\v 26 “Dere haariza boncho Filkises, Qalawodosa Lusiyoosappe; saroy nees gido.
\v 27 Hayssa addeza Ayhuda asati oykki wodhana gishin izi Oroome asi gididayssa ta gakka erida gish wotadaratara gakkada ashshadis.
\v 28 Isti iza aazas mootizakkonne ta erana koyada dere duulatakko shiishadis.
\v 29 Isti iza bolla shiishida mootoy ba woga gish gididayssa eradis; gido attin iza hayqos woykko qashos gaththiza miishi deenna.
\v 30 Hayssa addeza wodhanas asay maqetidayssa ta siyada heerakka siyida mala nekko yeddadis; mootizaytikka heen ne sinthan ba mooto shishshana mala istas yootadis” gides.
\p 
\v 31 Hessa gish wotadarati ba azazettida mala Phawuloosa qammara efidi Antiphaxxirose geetettizaso gaththida.
\v 32 Wontetha gallas toganchati Phawuloosara baana mala ooththidi isti qas guye so simmida.
\v 33 Toganchati gede Qisaariya gakkidi dabdaabeza dere haarizayssas immidi Phawuloosa iza sinth shiishida.
\v 34 Dere haarizayssi dabdaabeza nababidinne Phawuloosa “Ne awa dereppe yadii?” gi oychides. Izi Kilqiya dere as gididayssa eridi;
\v 35 “Nena mootizayti yishin ta ne yo7o siyana” gides; Herdoosa gibbe gaaththan izi naagettana mala azazides.
\c 24
\s1 Ayhuda asay Phawuloosa mootides
\p 
\v 1 Ichashu gallassafe guye Qeeseta halaqa Hananiyay issi issi cimataranne Xarxuloosa geetettiza xabaqara Qisaariya bides; istika dere ayssiza Filkisekko shiiqidi Phawuloosa mootida.
\v 2 Phawuloosi xeeygeti shiiqin Xarxuloossi iza hizgi mootides “Boncho Filkise! Nu ne baggara daro saroteth demmidos; ne lo7o aysonka nu deres lo7etethi beettides.
\p 
\v 3 “Hessa ne lo7o oosoza nu awan gidin aydekka dhoqu gida bonchoranne galatara ekkoos.
\v 4 Ta ha7i nena gam7isontanne daaburissonta qaanthara nees yootizayssa kiyatethan ne nu gizayssa siyana mala woossos.
\p 
\v 5 “Hayssi addezi nuus iita harge gidides; alamen diza Ayhudata ubba bolla meto medhees, Naaziraawe geetettiza wordo asata waanna kaalethizadey izakko.
\v 6 Izi Xoossa Keeththe tunisana gishin nu iza oykkidos. [Nu woga mala nu iza bolla pirdana qoppidos.
\v 7 Gido attin wotadarata halaqata azazizayssi Lusiyoossi gakkidi nu kusheppe iza wolqara woththi ekkides.
\v 8 Iza mootiza asaykka neekko yaana mala azazides.] Hayssi nu iza bolla shiishida mootozi wuri tumu gididayssa ne ne baggara iza oycha gakkanaas dandayassa” gides.
\p 
\v 9 Hinko Ayhuda asatikka “Ee hayssi yo7ozi wurikka tumukko” giidi ammanettida.
\s1 Phawuloosi bana ashshana oge medhides
\p 
\v 10 Dere ayssiza Filikkisey Phawuloosi haasayana mala ba kushera malati besides; Phawuloosikka “Ne daro wodesoppe hayssa dereza ayssizadde gididayssa ta eriza gish ta bolla shiiqida mootozas ta nees ufayssa zaaro shiishays.
\v 11 Ta Xoossas goynnanas Yerusalame biin hachchi tammanne nam7u gallassafe darontayssa ne ne baggara eranas dandayassa.
\v 12 Xoossa Keeththan gidin Ayhudata Woosa Keeththan woykko katama giddon ta oonarakka palametishin woykko dere giddon meto medhishin tana demmibetenna.
\v 13 Ha7i ta bolla isti shiishida mootozas ay markaka shishshanas dandayettenna.
\p 
\v 14 “Gido attin ta nees qoncisana koyizay isti wordo giza Goda ogera nu aawanta Xoossas gooynayssinne Muse woganne nabeta maxaafan xaafetidayssaka ubba ammanays.
\v 15 Istika ufays ooththiza mala takka nagaranchatinne xilloti hayqoppe dendanayssa Xoossan ammanettays.
\v 16 Hessa gish Xoossa sinthaninne asa sinthan sidhey baynda hanoy taas daana mala ubba wode minnays.
\p 
\v 17 “Ta Yerusalameppe kezin taas daro layth gididappe guye ta dere asas maado miishenne Xoossas imettiza miishe ekka yadis.
\v 18 Tana isti Xoossa Keeththan demmiday ta hessa gaththishinna; he wode ta geeyza woga polishin tanara daro asi deenna; ooshinne shiroykka deenna.
\v 19 Gido attin Iisiyappe yida issi issi Ayhuda asati deettes; istasika tana mootos gaththizazi diza gidikko ne sinthan tana mootetto.
\v 20 Hessafe guye ta duulata sinth shiiqikko ta ooththida qohoy diikko he asati yooteto.
\v 21 Tana hayssas gaththida gaasoy ta ista giddon eqqada ‘Hayqqidaytas denthi dees ga yootida gish hach pirdas inte sinth shiiqadis’ ta gaada qaala dhoqu hista yootadis attin hara ta ooththida miishi deenna” gides. \x * \xo 24:21 \xt Hawa 23:6\x*
\p 
\v 22 Filkisey Goda oge lo7ethi eriza gish “Wotadereta halaqata azazizayssa Lusiyoossi yiza wode ta inte yo7oza gish qasho gidiza yo7o immana” giidi ista yeddides.
\v 23 Phawuloosa naagiza mato halaqay “Iza daro waayssonta lo7etha naaga; iza laggeti izas koshshiza miishi ekki yiikko diggofa” gides.
\s1 Phawuloosi Filikkisenne Dirussilla sinth shiiqides
\p 
\v 24 Guuththa wodeppe kaallidi Filkisey Ayhuda as gidida ba macheyo Durissillara yides; Phawuloosakka xeygidi Yesus Kirstoosan ammano gish izi yootishin siydes.
\v 25 Phawuloosi xillotetha gish, asi barka bana haaro gishshinne buroppe yaana pirda gish yootin Filkisey babbidi “Ha7i ne ba; hara wode taas giigishin ta nena xeeyga ekkana” gides.
\v 26 Filkisey Phawuloosappe gubbo ekkanas ufaysi ooththi naagida gish daro wode gakkanaas xeygi xeygi hasayssides.
\p 
\v 27 Nam7u laythafe guye Phorqiyossa Fisxoossi Filkise ollan shuumettides; Filkisey Ayhudata ufayssanas koydi Phawuloosa qashoson aggagides.
\c 25
\s1 Phawuloosi ba yo7oza Oroome kawoy beyana mala oychides
\p 
\v 1 Fisxoossi ba ayssiza dere Qisaariya gelidi heedzdzu gallas aqetidi heeppe Yerusalame bides.
\v 2-3 Heen diza Qeeseta halaqatinne issi issi Ayhudata giddofe gita gita asati Phawuloosa bolla ba mooto shiishida; “Phawuloosa ha Yerusalame ehidi nuus lo7o ooso ooththarki!” giidi woossida; isti hessa giday Phawuloosa naagidi oge bolla wodhanas koyda gishassa.
\v 4 Gido attin Fisxoossi “Phawuloosi Qisaariyan qasho keeththan naagetes; takka ha7i elle simmada he izakko baana.
\v 5 Inte giddofe daannateththi dizayti tanara Qisaariya betto; Phawuloosi ooththida qohoy diza gidikko heen mooteto” gides.
\p 
\v 6 Fisxoossi osupun woykko tammu gallassafe daronta wode istara gam7idappe guye Qisaariya bides; he gakkida mala wontetha gallas pirda wombora bolla uttidi Phawuloosa izakko shiishana mala azazides.
\v 7 Phawuloosi iza sinth shiiqin Yerusalameppe yida Ayhudati Phawuloosa giddoththidi markay baynda daro deexo mooto iza bolla shiishida.
\p 
\v 8 Phawuloosikka “Tani Ayhuda woga bolla gidin Xoossa Keeththa bolla woykko Oroome Kawo Qeesare bollaka gaththida qohoy deenna” giidi ista mootoza shaariza zaaro istas immides.
\p 
\v 9 Gido attin Fisxoossi Ayhudata ufayssanas koydi Phawuloosa “Ne Yerusalame baada hayssa yo7oza heen ta sinthan pirdettana koyay?” gides.
\v 10 Phawuloosi qasse hizgidi izas zaarides “Hekko ta pirdettanas taas bessiza Qeesare pirda wombora sinthan eqqadis; nekka lo7etha eriza mala ta Ayhudata bolla ooththida aykko qohoykka deenna.
\v 11 Ta qohida gidikko woykko tana hayqos gaththiza qoho ta ooththida gidikko ta hayqoppe attana giikke; gido attin isti shiishshiza mootoy mela hada gidikko oonikka tana istas aaththi immanas dandayenna; takka ta yo7oy Qeesare sinth shiiqana mala ‘Yigibayne’ gadis.”
\p 
\v 12 Hessa wode Fisxoossi bana zorizaytara hasayettidi “Ne Qeesarekko ‘Yigibayne’ giza gidikko Qeesarekko baandasa” gides.
\s1 Phawuloosi Agirpha sinthinne Barniqqe sinth shiiqides
\p 
\v 13 Guuththa gallassatappe guye kawo Agirphaynne Barniqey Fisxoosa “Hashshu lo7on yadassa” gi mokkanas gede Qisaariya bida.
\v 14 Isti heen daro gallas uttida gish Fisxoossi Phawuloosa yo7oza Kawo Agirphas hizgi yootides “Filkisey qasho keeththan yeggi aggida issadey haan dees.
\v 15 Ta Yerusalamen diza wode Qeeseta halaqatinne Ayhudata ciimati ha addeza yo7o taakko ehidi ta iza bolla pirdana mala oychida.
\v 16 Ta qasse ‘Mootetidadey mootizayta sinthan eqqidi bana mootiza yo7ozas bessiza zaaro immoonta dishin mootetidade aaththi imoy Oroome kawoteththas woga gidenna’ gaada zaaradis.
\p 
\v 17 “Hessa gish iza mootizayti shiiqetidi yida mala heerakka wontetha gallas pirda womboran uttada Phawuloosa ta sinth shiishana mala azazadis.
\v 18 Iza mootizayti iza achchan eqqida wode isti iza bolla shiishida mootoy ta baggara izi iita oosonta aggenna gaada qoppida mala gidibenna.
\v 19 Gido attin isti izara mootetizay ba ammano gishshinne Phawuloosi issi hayqqidayssa ‘Paxa dees’ giza Yesusa gish gidides.
\v 20 Takka hessa mala yo7o qora xeellanas tana metida gish Phawuloosa ‘Ne Yerusalame baada hessa yo7oza heen pirdettana koyay?’ gadis.
\v 21 Hizgin izi qasse yo7ozi Oroome kawo sinthan beyettana mala koydi ‘Ta yo7oy Qeessare sinth shiiqana mala oychays’ gida gish iza yo7o Qeesarekko ta yeddana gakkanaas izi qasho keeththan gam7ana mala azazadis” gides.
\p 
\v 22 Agirphay Fisxoosa “Takka izi giza siyana koyays” gides. Fisxoosikka “Wonto siyandassa” gides.
\p 
\v 23 Hessa gish wontetha gallas Agirphaynne Barniqey kawoti may7iza mayo may7idinne daro bonchora wotadarata halaqataranne he kataman diza gita asatan azhabetti yiidi pirda keeththe gelida. Hessafe guye Fisxoossi Phawuloosa xeygisides.
\v 24 Fisxoossi hizgides “Kawo Agirpha, qas nunara diza asato! Ayhuda asati wuri ‘Hayssi addezi hayssafe guye paxa daana bessenna’ giidi waassishe Yerusalamenka haanka iza bolla pirdettana mala isti tana oychizay hayssa inte beyiza addeza gishassa.
\v 25 Ta ta baggara iza hayqos gaththiza issi balakka iza bolla demmabekke. Izi ‘Ta yo7oy Oroome kawo sinth shiiqi beyetto’ gida gish ta iza he yeddanas qachadis.
\p 
\v 26 “Gido attin iza gish tani ta godas xaafana giza erettida yo7oy deenna; hessa gish iza issi issi paace oyshota oychikko taas xaafanayssi daanakkonne gaada inteko, harappeka kawo Agirpha neekko shiishadis.
\v 27 Gaasoyka qasho asi pude bollatiza dhoqa daannakko bishin izi mootetiza yo7o qoncisonta aggoy asa eeya kessizayssi taas beettides” gides.
\c 26
\s1 Phawuloosi kawo Agirpha sinthan yootida yo7o
\p 
\v 1 Agirphi Phawuloosa “Neni ne gish haasayanas dandayassa” gides. Phawuloosikka ba kushe denthidi zaaro hizgi immides.
\v 2 “Kawo Agirpha! Tana Ayhudati mootiza yo7o ubbas hach ta ne sinthan tana maaddana zaaro immiza gish tana daro ufaysses.
\v 3 Gaasoyka ne Ayhudata woganne ista palama ubba lo7etha eraasa; hessa gish ne ta giza ubba dandayada siyana mala ta nena woossays.
\p 
\v 4 “Tani guuththa natetha wodeppe doommada waana de7idakko Ayhuda asati eretes. Koyroppe ha7i gakkanaas tani ta dere asa giddoninne Yerusalamen ta de7ida duussi asay erees.
\v 5 Qasseka isti markattana koykko nu ammano gish ta keeha mintha woga naagiza Farsaawe bagga gidada gam7iddadde gididayssa isti koyroppe denthidi eretes. \x * \xo 26:5 \xt Hawa 23:6; Pili 3:5\x*
\v 6 Ha7i qasse pirdas tana hayssan essiday Xoossi kase nu aawatas immida caaqo qaala ufaysa gishassa.
\v 7 Ha ufayssakko gakkanaas nu zarketi tammanne nam7ati Xoossa gallassinne qamma goynnishe naagida. Kawo intes hoola! Ayhudati tana mootizay ha yo7oza gishassa.
\v 8 Xoossi hayqqidayta denthanayssi waanidi Ayhuda gidida inte achchan ammanetibenee?
\p 
\v 9 “Takka ta baggara Naazirete Yesusa sunthas eqqetanas bessees gaada qoppadis shin; \x * \xo 26:9 \xt Hawa 8:3; 22:4-5\x*
\v 10 tani Yerusalamen ooththidaykka hessakoshin; Qeeseta halaqatappe ta ekkida godateththara ammanizaytappe darota qasho keeththan yeggiissadis; ista wodhishin wodhizaytara issife days.
\v 11 Daro wode Ayhudata Woosa Keeththati dizason awanka isti qaaxayettana malanne ba ammano kadana mala ooththadis; ista bolla daro hanqetadakka Isra7eeleppe karen diza hara katamataka baada ammanizayta gooddadis.
\s1 Phawuloosi Kirstoosakko waani simmidakko yootides
\p 
\v 12 “Hayssa ha yo7ozas Qeeseta hallaqatappe kumeththa godateththinne azazo ekkada Damasqo geetettizaso ta bishin;
\v 13 Kawo intes hoola! Buro ta ogen dishin gadey seeta gallas gidishin awa arshe poo7oppe aadhdhiza poo7o beyadis; he poo7oy tananne tanara biza asata yuuy aadhdhidi saloppe poo7ides.
\v 14 Nu wurikka biitta bolla kundi dishin Ayhudata qaalara ‘Sawule! Sawule! Tana aazas goodday? Neni qara mashsha bolla eqqiikko nerka nena qohassa’ giza qaala siyadis.
\p 
\v 15 “Takka ‘Godo! Ne oonee?’ gadis; Godayka ‘Tani ne, gooddiza Yesusakko!
\v 16 Ha7i dendada ne tohon eqqa; ta nees qonciday ne tana ha7i beyidayssaninne sinthafe ta nena bessanayssan ne taas markattizade gidana mala ta nena shuumana koyadis.
\v 17 Isra7eele asa kusheppenne ta nena istako kiittiza Ayzaabeta kusheppekka ashshana.
\v 18 Ne ista ayfe doyana malanne dhumappe poo7on kessana mala qasseka Xala7es haarettizasoppe Xoossakko ne zaarana mala ooththana; istika tana ammanida gish ba nagarappe maarettana qasse doorettidayta giddon isti laata gade demmana’ gides.
\s1 Phawuloosi ba ooso gish yootides
\p 
\v 19 “Hessa gish kawo Agirpha! Saloppe taas imettida ajjutaas ta azazettadis.
\v 20 Gido attin ta kasetada Damasqon diza asa kaalethada Yerusalameninne Yuhuda deren ubban dizayta qasseka Ayzaabetikka nagara ogeppe Xoossakko simmidi maarettana mala erisadis; isti nagarappe simmidayssa bessizazi ooththana mala ta istas yootadis. \x * \xo 26:20 \xt Hawa 9:20,28-29\x*
\v 21 Hessa gaason Ayhudati ta Xoossa Keeththan dishin tana oykkidi wodhana koyda.
\v 22 Hachchi gakkanaaska taas Xoossafe maadoy pacci erenna. Hessa gish guuththaska gitaska markatashe hayssan eqqadis. Nabetinne Musey kasetidi hayssa malay hanana gidayssa yootoppe attin ta hara aykkokka yootabeykke.
\v 23 Istika yootidayssi ‘Xoossi kiittidadey meto beyana. Hayqoppe dendon koyro gididi asi attana poo7o Isra7eele deressinne Ayzaabetas qoncana’ gizayssa” gides. \x * \xo 26:23 \xt 1Qoro 15:20; Isa 42:6; 49:6\x*
\p 
\v 24 Phawuloosi hessa yootishin Fisxoossi “Phawuloosa! Ha7i ne gooyonta aggaka; ne daro tamaridayssi nena gooshshides” gi waassides.
\p 
\v 25 Phawuloosi gidikko izas “Boncho Fisxoosa! Ta nees tuma erada yootays attin gooyabeykke.
\v 26 Ta iza sinthan qoncera yootida kawoy hayssa yo7oza erees; hayssika qotara ooththetontayssa gidida gish kawoy eranayssa ta ammanettays.
\v 27 Kawo Agirpha! Nabeta ammanasa gidikkii? Ne ammanizayssa ta erays” gi zaarides.
\p 
\v 28 Agirphayka Phawuloosa “Hekko ne tana hanno guuththa wode giddon ammanthana koyasa” gides.
\v 29 Phawuloosikka izas zaaridi “Guuththa woden gidinka woykko daro woden ne xalla gidonta dishin hach ta yootidayssa siyiday wuri hanno ta qashetethaya atta wurikka ta mala gidana mala ta Xoossa woossays” gides.
\p 
\v 30 Hessafe guye kawoy, dere ayssizayssi, Barniqeynne istara uttida asaykka wuri dendides.
\v 31 Isti heeppe kezi bishe ba giddon “Hayssi addezi hayqos woykko qashos gaththiza miishe aykkokka ooththibenna” gida.
\v 32 Agirphayka Fisxoosa “Hayssi addezi yo7oza Qeesares shiiqo goontakko aykko wosoy baynda mela yedetanako shin” gides.
\c 27
\s1 Phawuloosi Oroome bides
\p 
\v 1 Nuni Xaalane dere markaben baana mala geetetti qashettida gish Phawuloosanne hara qasho asataka kawo Awugisxoosa wotadaratappe gidida Yuuliyoosa geetettiza mato halaqas aaththi immida.
\v 2 Iisiya abba achchan diza dereta biza markaben gelidi bidos. Tasolonqen diza issi Maqidooniya as Arisxirokoosa geetettizayssi nunara dees.
\p 
\v 3 Wontetha gallas Sidoona gizaso gakkidos; Yuuliyoossi Phawuloosas lo7o gidida gish Phawuloosi ba laggetakko biidi asay izas koshshiza maado ooththana mala piqade immides.
\v 4 Heeppe dendi nu bishin sintha baggara carkoy nu bolla carkiza gish abba giddon diza Qophiroose deren gemmetidi gede sinthe bidos.
\v 5 Kilqiya gizasonne Phinfiliya geetettiza dere achchan diza abba pinnidi Looqiya deren diza Muura geetettiza katama gakkidos.
\v 6 Heen mato halaqay Ixaaliya dere biza Iskindiriya dere markabe demmidi nuna izan gelthides.
\p 
\v 7 Daro gallas loddu gi gi biidi daro waayetidi Qandoose geetettiza katama achchi gakkidos; carkoykka nu sinth boonta mala diggin Salmoona achchara aadhdhidi Qarxeese geetettiza abba giddon diza deren gemettidi bidos.
\v 8 Daro waayetidi lanqe lanqe oykki nu aadhdhidappe guye Laasiya geetettiza katama achchan diza “Lo7o” geetettiza markabey eqqizaso gakkidos. \f + \fr 27:8 \fq lanqe \ft gizayssi abba giddon diza Qarxeese gaxa guussa.\f*
\p 
\v 9 Nu biza oge bolla daro daaburan xooma wodey aadhdhida gish ha7i abba bolla baanas daro meto gidida gish Phawuloosi banara diza asay naagettana mala hizgides;
\v 10 “Aso! Hayssafe nu kaallidi baana buussay daro metora dizayssi taas bettes; markabezan diza caanaaza bollanne markabeza bolla xalala gidonta asa shempo bollaka gita qohoy gakkana.”
\v 11 Mato halaqay qas Phawuloosa zoreppe bollara markabeza laaggiza waannazinne marakabeza goday gizayssa siydes.
\v 12 He markabey eqqizasoy balgoy aadhdhana gakkanaas markabes lo7o shemposo gidonta gish dariza bagga asay “Hammutha sinth gujjanas dandayettikko awa arshey wullizasoppe dugeha baggaranne pudeha baggara diza Finqe geetettizaso Qarxeese markabe shemposo nu gakkidi balgo heen aaththoos” giidi ba qofa shiishida.
\s1 Abba bolla dambalay dendides
\p 
\v 13 Dugeha baggara guuththa carkoy carkishin beyidi isti qoppida mala hanana misatin baana kezida; markabey eqqizasoppe baana dendidi Qarxeese achchara lanqe lanqe oykkidi aadhdhi bida.
\v 14 Gido attin guuththa wodeppe guye “Awa arshey mokizasoppe pudehappe yiza gote carko” geetettiza iita wolqama carkoy abba giddon diza dereyippe dendidi istako abba giddo yides.
\v 15 Markabeza carkoy sugin carkara eqqeettanas dandayonta ixin nu co7u giidi carkoy efizaso bidos.
\v 16 Qeedda geetettiza abba giddonko diza dere dizaarin geemettidi nu bishin daro waayetidi markabeza qeeri wogoloyin oykkidi essanas dandayidos.
\v 17 Markabeza laagizayti qeeri wogoloyo markabezako goochchi kessidi markabeza wodorora xaaxida. Markabezikka Sirtise geetettiza abba accey dari dizason kundonta mala babbidi iza bolla diza shara woththidi carkon laageti bida.
\v 18 Gote carkoy minni bida gish wontetha gallas markabezan caanettida miishata issa issa abba giddo yegeth oykkida.
\v 19 Heedzdzantho gallas markabezas koshshiza miishataka ba kushera kessi kessi yeggida.
\v 20 Daro wode gakkanaas awa arsheka xoolinteka beyonta aggida gishshinne carkoyka kaseppe minni minni biza gish hayssafe guye nu attana dandayokko giza qofan ufays qanxidos.
\p 
\v 21 Asay kath moonta daro gallas uttides. Hessa gish Phawuloosi asa giddon eqqidi “Ha asato! Inte ta gizayssa siydi Qarxeeseppe dendontakko ha qohoynne ha dhayoy inte bolla gakkenakkoshin.
\v 22 Ha7ikka markabezi xalla qohettana attin intefe issade shempoykka dhayenna. Hessa gish aykkoy baawa; babbofte gaada intena zorays.
\v 23 Qamma omars ta izas gidida ta goynniza Xoossay kiittida kiitanchay ta achchan eqqidi
\v 24 ‘Phawuloosa! Babbofa! ne Qeesare sinthan eqqana bessees; hekko nenara issife bizayta wursi Xoossi ne gish hayqoppe ashshana’ giidi taas yootides.
\v 25 Hessa gish inteno ha asato aykkoy baawa; Xoossi taas hayssa yootidayssa polanayssa ta ammanays.
\v 26 Gidikkoka hayssi gote carkozi gede issi abba giddon diza dere achchi efidi nuna yeggana” gides.
\p 
\v 27 Tammanne oydantho qamma Andiriya Abba giddon carkoy nuna waayssishin bishe leela giddoth markabeza laaggizaytas abbafe biitta bolla gakkida misatides. \f + \fr 27:27 \fq Andirya Abba \ft Mediteraniya abbafe issi baggara diza abba.\f*
\v 28 Hessa gish abba ciimmateththi eranas abban yeggi xeelliza wodoro isti yeggi xeellishin; abba ciimmateththi oyddu tammu metre keena gidi beettides; gam7ishe Ha7ikka yeggin heedzdzu tammu metre keena ciimma gididayssa demmida.
\v 29 Nu diza markabey abba gaxan diza zaalla shuchchara icetonta mala babbidi markabezappe guye baggara markabey qaaxonta mala naagiza dhishikke duge abba giddo yeggida. Hessafe guye istas qamay wontana mala woossa oykkida.
\v 30 Markabeza laagizayti markabezappe kezidi baqatana koyda gish markabezappe sintha baggara markabe naagiza dhishikke yeggiza misatidi markabeza bolla diza qeeri wogoloyo duge abba giddo yeggida.
\v 31 Hessa wode Phawuloosi mato halaqanne wotadarata “Hayti markabezan diza asati markabeza bolla shempidi uttonta aggikko inteka attana dandayekketa” gides.
\v 32 Hessa gish wotadarati wogoloyo oykkida wodoroza qanxi yeggin iza abba bolla tokkettana mala yeddi aggida.
\p 
\v 33 Gadey wontana gishin wurikka kath maana mala Phawuloosi ista hizgi woossides “Inte aazi hananesha giidi hirgan kath moonta aggin hachchi tammanne oydantho gallasa.
\v 34 Hessa gish inte kath maana mala ta intena woossays. Inte miikko minnana; mulekka aykko qohoykka inte bolla gakkenna” gides.
\v 35 Izi hessa gidappe guye kath ekkidi Xoosse galatidi asa ubba sinthan kathi muus oykkides.
\v 36 Hessa wode wurikka minetidi kath mida.
\v 37 Markabeza giddon diza asay wuri nam7u xeetanne laapun tammanne usuppuna.
\v 38 Wurikka mi kaallidappe guye markaban caanettida gisteza duge abba giddo yeggidi markabeza deexo kawushshida.
\s1 Markabezi meqides
\p 
\v 39 Gadey wontin ba dizaso eribeetenna. Gido attin accey dizaso abba kurqunthu demmida. Istas dandayettizakko markabeza he sugi shishshana qoppida.
\v 40 Markabeza oykkiza dhishikke qanxidi abba giddo yeggida. He wode markabe laggiza miisha oykkida wodorota birshida. Ha baggara diza shaara carko bagga dhoqu histidi kezana abba gaxa bida.
\v 41 Gido attin markabezi daro accey koretti uttidayssara icetidi duge gufannides; sintha bolla duge gufanni dhishikketidi qaaxontayssa gidides. Qas abba dambalay daroppe dendidayssan guye baggara meqereteth oykkides.
\p 
\v 42 Qasho asappe issadeyka abban wodhdhidi kessi ekkonta mala wotadarati wodhana qoppida.
\v 43 Mato halaqay qas Phawuloosa ashshanas koyda gish ista qofa ekkana koybenna. Gido attin haathe wodhdhi erizayti markabezappe duge abban guppi guppi wodhdhidi gede biitta bolla kezana mala azazides.
\p 
\v 44 Hanko attidayti meqi wodhdhida sanqa bolla abba pinnana mala azazides; hessatho hanidi wurikka saron abba giddofe biitta bolla gakkida.
\c 28
\s1 Phawuloosi Melaaxiya biittan
\p 
\v 1 Nu Biittay dizaso sarotethan gakkidappe guye nu gakkida abba giddon diza derey Melaaxiya geetettiza dere gididaro eridos.
\v 2 He dereyin diza asay daro malalisiza kiyateth nuus ooththides. He wode iray bukkida gishshinne meeggo gidida gish tama eththidi nuna mokki ekkida.
\v 3 Phawuloosi afira giza mithi shiishshidi taman gujin tama seelappe dendidayssan shooshi kezidi iza kushe bolla xaaxxetides. \f + \fr 28:3 \fq afira giza mithi \ft gizayssi issi issi Gamo asati qayxare, hunxe mithith geettes.\f*
\v 4 Malta asay shooshi Phawuloosa kushe bolla xaaxxetidayssa beyidi “Hayssi addezi shempo wodhidade; gaasoyka abba dambalappekka izi attidi yikkokka pirdiza Xoossafe kessi ekkidi paxa daana dandaybenna” giidi ba giddon haasayettida
\v 5 Phawuloosi qas shoosha duge taman qoqof yeggidi aykkokka hanibenna.
\v 6 Asaykka “Aydeppe ayde iza asatethay kixxanesha; woykko qopponta kundidi hayqqana” giidi naagides; gido attin isti daro wode naagishin iza bolla aykkoynne hanontayssa beyidi ba qofa lammidi “Hayssi addezi xoossa!” gides.
\p 
\v 7 He nu dizaso matan abba giddon diza dereyo ayssiza Puppulyoosa geetettizades gadey dees; he addezi nuna mokki ekkidi bason heedzdzu gallas gakkanaas lo7ethi imattides.
\v 8 Heen Puppulyoosa aawa miishaynne guso hargey sakkin ichchidi dees; Phawuloosi izakko gelidi izas woossidessinne iza bolla ba kushe woththidi pathides.
\v 9 Hessi hessatho hanidappe guye he dereyn diza hara harganchati yiidi paxida.
\v 10 Asaykka nuus daro miish ehidi nuna bonchizayssa nuna bessida; nu markaben baana dendin nuus koshshizayssa markaben wursi caanida.
\s1 Phawuloosi Milixineppe Oroome bides
\p 
\v 11 Nu Milixinen heedzdzu agina gam7idappe guye balgoy aadhdhana gakkanaas abba giddon diza dereyin gam7idi Iskindiriyappe yiza markaben gelidi baana dendidos; he markabeza bolla Diyossiqoroosa geetettiza nam7u mente eeqata misiley dees.
\v 12 Gede Sirakuuse geetettiza katama gakkidi heen heedzdzu gallas gam7idos.
\v 13 Heeppe abba bollara biidi Regiyoome geetettiza katama gakkidos; heen issi gallas aqidi duge baggara yiza carkoy carkida gish nam7antho gallas Puttiyoloose geetettizaso bidos.
\v 14 Heen ammanizayta demmidi istara nu laapun gallas gakkanaas uttana mala nuna woossida. Heeppe qasse Oroome bidos.
\v 15 Oroomen diza ammaniza asay nu gish siydi Apiyoose geetettiza giyanne “Heedzdzu Aqosota” geetettizaso gakkanaas nuna mokkana yida; Phawuloosaykka ista beyidi Xoosse galatidessinne minetides.
\s1 Phawuloosi Oroomen
\p 
\v 16 Nuni Oroome gelida wode Phawuloosa naaganas issi wotadaray izas imettin Phawuloosi barka daana mala izas fiiqadey imettides.
\p 
\v 17 Heedzdzu gallassafe guye Phawuloosi Oroomen diza Ayhudatappe gita asata baako xeygisides; istika izakko shiiqin “Ta ishato! Tani Isra7eele dere bollanne nu aawata woga bolla ooththida issi qohoykka deenna; gido attin Yerusalamen tana qachidi Oroome asatas aaththi immida.
\v 18 Oroome asati tana qori oychidappe guye tana hayqos gaththiza miish demmoonta aggida gish birshi yeddana koyda.
\v 19 Gido attin Ayhuda asay ta bolla issi wosoy baynda yeddetonta mala eqqettin ta yo7oy Qeesare sinth shiiqidi beetto gaanas taas gidde gidides. Gido attin tani ta dereta mootiza gaasoy taas deenna.
\v 20 Ta qas ha7i intena xeygisiday intena beyanassinne hanno intes yootanassa. Hayssa sansalatan tani qashetiday Isra7eele naytas imettida ufaysa gaasonna” gides.
\p 
\v 21 Istika izas “Ne gish Yuhuda dereppe xaafetida debiddabbey nuna gakkibeenna. Ha yida asatappe oonikka ne gish iita haasayiday baawa.
\v 22 Hayssa ne kaalliza ammanoza gish awanka asay iita haasayizayssa nu eroos. Hessa gish ne qofay azakkonne nu siyana koyoos” gi zaarida.
\p 
\v 23 Bare izas immidi hara gallas kushe kumidi izi diza keeththe yida. Izikka maladoppe omars gakkanaas Xoossa Kawoteththa gish markatethan ba qofa istas qoncisides. Muse wogappenne nabeta maxaafatappe xaqasi xaqasi Yesusa gish istas qoncisi yootides.
\v 24 Istafe issi issi asati izi yootida qaala ammanida; baggayti qas ammanibetenna.
\v 25 Istika ba giddon issoy issara qofan gaggonta shaaketida; Phawuloosi wursethan yootishe “Xillo Ayanay nabe Isayaasa baggara kase inte aawatas yootidayssi tumakko!
\v 26 Izi yootida qaalay,
\q2 ‘Hayssa derakko baada inte sisi siyana shin yuushi qoppeketa,
\q3 ayfera beyana shin woznan wotheketa gaada yoota.
\q1 
\v 27 Gaasoyka he asata woznay muumides,
\q3 ista haythayka tullides;
\q3 ista ayfey qooqides.
\q2 Hessatho hanontakko
\q3 isti ba ayfera beyidi
\q3 ba haythara siydi ba woznan yuushi qoppidi
\q2 taakko ha simmananne
\q3 takka ista pathanashin’ gides.
\p 
\v 28 “Histikko Xoossi as ashshiza kiitay Ayzaabetaska kiitettidayssa inte erite; istika ero giidi ekkettes” gides.
\v 29 Phawuloosi hessa yootidappe guye Ayhuda asati ba giddon daro palametishe kezi bida. \f + \fr 28:29 \ft Issi issi Geeshsha Maxaafatan paydo 29 bolla diza qofay gujettibenna.\f*
\p 
\v 30 Phawuloosi kiratida keeththan nam7u layth kumeth de7ides; baako yiza as wursi mokki ekkides.
\v 31 Xoossa kawoteth sabakon Goda Yesus Kirstoosa gish oonikka iza diggonta xalatethara asa tamarsides.
